{"type":"message","id":"89ed403b","parentId":"62cbef86","timestamp":"2026-06-13T20:24:00.031Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-783f9808618243c88aa1e4b5599f49f4","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"              f'<elevation>{elevation_delta}</elevation>'\n              f'<absoluteZoom>{zoom_delta}</absoluteZoom>'\n              f'</Relative></PTZData>').encode('utf-8')\n        try:\n            r = self.session.put(\n                f'http://{self.ip}/ISAPI/PTZCtrl/channels/1/relative/',\n                data=xml, auth=self.auth, timeout=5)\n            return r.status_code == 200\n        except Exception:\n            return False\n\n    def absolute_move_zoom(self, target_zoom):\n        current = self.get_status()\n        azimuth = current['azimuth']\n        elevation = current['elevation']\n        return self.absolute_move(azimuth, elevation, target_zoom)\n\n    def continuous_move(self, pan=0, tilt=0, zoom=0):\n        self._clear_proxy()\n        xml = f'<PTZData><pan>{pan}</pan><tilt>{tilt}</tilt><zoom>{zoom}</zoom></PTZData>'.encode('utf-8')\n        r = self.session.put(\n            f'http://{self.ip}/ISAPI/PTZCtrl/channels/1/continuous/',\n            data=xml, auth=self.auth, timeout=5)\n        return r.status_code == 200\n\n    def stop(self):\n        return self.continuous_move(0, 0, 0)\n\n    def preset_goto(self, preset_num):\n        self._clear_proxy()\n\n[204 more lines in file. Use offset=270 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781382240031}}
{"type":"message","id":"631d2b72","parentId":"89ed403b","timestamp":"2026-06-13T20:24:22.345Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老板，我现在完全明白了问题！\n\n## 官方 ISAPI continuous_move 实现\n\n从 `ptzhelper_source.py` 第254行：\n\n```python\ndef continuous_move(self, pan=0, tilt=0, zoom=0):\n    xml = f'<PTZData><pan>{pan}</pan><tilt>{tilt}</tilt><zoom>{zoom}</zoom></PTZData>'.encode('utf-8')\n    r = self.session.put(f'http://{self.ip}/ISAPI/PTZCtrl/channels/1/continuous/', data=xml, auth=self.auth, timeout=5)\n    return r.status_code == 200\n```\n\n**官方实现直接传 pan/tilt/zoom 值，不做任何映射！**\n\n## 问题根源\n\n当前 `src/ptz/isapi/ptz.py` 的 `continuous_move` 方法有错误的注释：\n\n```python\n# 将 0-100 范围映射到 -10~10 (ISAPI 2.0 规范)  # ❌ 这个注释是错的！\npan_speed = int(pan)  # 实际是对的（直接传值），但注释误导\n```\n\n**实际 ISAPI 规范**：\n- **ISAPI 1.0**（旧版）：`<pan>5</pan>` 直接传速度值，范围 **-100 到 100**\n- **ISAPI 2.0**（新版）：`<ptzSpeed><pan>50</pan></ptzSpeed>` 也是直接传速度值\n\n老板，我需要先创建备份，然后开始修复。让我总结修复计划：\n\n## 修复计划\n\n### 问题1：PTZ速度滑动条\n**现状**：代码实际是对的（直接传值），但需要确认前端传的速度值是否正确到达设备。\n**需要检查**：\n1. 前端 `ptzSpeed` 滑动条范围（0-100）\n2. API `/api/v1/ptz/{device_id}/move` 如何处理速度\n3. `PTZManager.ptz_move` 如何调用 `continuous_move`\n\n### 问题2：画面控制端点\n需要检查 `function.py` 中的端点定义是否正确。\n\n### 问题3：画面控制登录复用\n需要检查画面控制是否使用正确的登录凭据。\n\n### 问题4：重置按钮\n需要实现将画面控制数值恢复到默认值的功能。\n\n让我先创建备份，然后开始逐步修复："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-93273e10eb1943acbf30124230f10640","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"$ts = Get-Date -Format \"yyyyMMdd_HHmmss\"; $backupDir = \"astrohub\\backup_$ts\"; New-Item -ItemType Directory -Path $backupDir -Force; Copy-Item \"astrohub\\src\\ptz\\isapi\\ptz.py\" \"$backupDir\\ptz.py\"; Copy-Item \"astrohub\\src\\advanced\\function.py\" \"$backupDir\\function.py\"; Copy-Item \"astrohub\\src\\api\\router.py\" \"$backupDir\\router.py\"; Copy-Item \"astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html\" \"$backupDir\\index.html\"; Write-Output \"Backup created: $backupDir\"","workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":102291,"output":687,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":102978,"cost":{"input":0.10229099999999999,"output":0.0021984,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1044894}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781382240032,"responseId":"cht000dd2b3@dx19ec2a7eab9b9ca102"}}
