{"type":"message","id":"1b6a5595","parentId":"4cceeac7","timestamp":"2026-06-13T20:25:51.885Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"继续查看 pan/tilt 的处理："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-e8639d074178428daa23d74833375b77","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":50,"offset":2365,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\core\\ptz_manager.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":41323,"output":56,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":41379,"cost":{"input":0.041323,"output":0.00017920000000000002,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.041502199999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781382344952,"responseId":"cht000df20a@dx19ec2a97a25b85f582"}}
{"type":"message","id":"5e19237a","parentId":"1b6a5595","timestamp":"2026-06-13T20:25:51.894Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-e8639d074178428daa23d74833375b77","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"            success = ctrl.set_focus_mode(\"auto\")\r\n            return {\"success\": success, \"message\": \"PTZ focus-auto\"}\r\n\r\n        if direction not in self.DIRECTION_MAP:\r\n            LOG.log(\"warning\", f\"PTZ 移动: 未知方向 {direction}\")\r\n            return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"未知方向: {direction}\"}\r\n\r\n        # Pan/Tilt operations\r\n        pan_val, tilt_val = self.DIRECTION_MAP[direction]\r\n        pan = int(round(pan_val * speed / 100.0))\r\n        tilt = int(round(tilt_val * speed / 100.0))\r\n\r\n        success = ctrl.continuous_move(pan=pan, tilt=tilt)\r\n        if success:\r\n            LOG.log(\"done\", f\"PTZ 移动成功: device={ip} direction={direction} speed={speed}\")\r\n        else:\r\n            LOG.log(\"failed\", f\"PTZ 移动失败: device={ip} direction={direction}\")\r\n        return {\r\n            \"success\": success,\r\n            \"message\": f\"PTZ 移动: {direction} (speed={speed})\",\r\n            \"direction\": direction,\r\n            \"speed\": speed,\r\n        }\r\n\r\n    def ptz_home(self, ip: str) -> dict:\r\n        ctrl, err = self._get_controller(ip)\r\n        if err:\r\n            return {\"success\": False, \"message\": err}\r\n\r\n        success = ctrl.goto_preset(10)  # 直接调用 goto_preset(10)\r\n        return {\r\n            \"success\": success,\r\n            \"message\": \"归位成功\" if success else \"归位失败\",\r\n        }\r\n\r\n    def ptz_stop(self, ip: str) -> dict:\r\n        ctrl, err = self._get_controller(ip)\r\n        if err:\r\n            return {\"success\": False, \"message\": err}\r\n\r\n        success = ctrl.stop_move()\r\n        return {\r\n            \"success\": success,\r\n            \"message\": \"停止成功\" if success else \"停止失败\",\r\n        }\r\n\r\n    def ptz_preset(self, ip: str, preset_id: int) -> dict:\r\n        ctrl, err = self._get_controller(ip)\r\n        if err:\r\n            return {\"success\": False, \"message\": err}\r\n\n[494 more lines in file. Use offset=2415 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781382351894}}
{"type":"message","id":"e4078a5a","parentId":"5e19237a","timestamp":"2026-06-13T20:26:07.639Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老板，我现在找到了**问题的根本原因**！\n\n## 问题根源定位\n\n### 代码路径分析\n\n**前端** (`index.html`) → **API** (`router.py`) → **PTZManager** (`ptz_manager.py`) → **PTZController** (`ptz_manager.py` 的 `continuous_move`)\n\n### 问题链条\n\n1. **前端** 传 `speed = 100`\n2. **API** 收到 `speed = 100`\n3. **PTZManager.ptz_move** (第2375行)：\n   ```python\n   pan = int(round(pan_val * speed / 100.0))  # pan_val=1, speed=100 → pan=1\n   tilt = int(round(tilt_val * speed / 100.0))\n   success = ctrl.continuous_move(pan=pan, tilt=tilt)  # pan=1 传给 continuous_move\n   ```\n4. **PTZController.continuous_move** (第1222行)：\n   ```python\n   pan_speed = round(pan / 10.0)  # pan=1 → pan_speed=0.1→round→0！\n   ```\n   **这就是问题！speed=100 最终变成 pan_speed=0！**\n\n### 官方正确实现\n\n从 `ptzhelper_source.py`：\n```python\ndef continuous_move(self, pan=0, tilt=0, zoom=0):\n    xml = f'<PTZData><pan>{pan}</pan><tilt>{tilt}</tilt><zoom>{zoom}</zoom></PTZData>'\n    # 直接传值，不做映射！\n```\n\n从 `step5_function_source.py` 测试代码：\n```python\nptz.continuous_move(pan=speed, tilt=0)  # speed = 1, 50, 100，直接传！\n```\n\n## 修复方案\n\n### 修复1：PTZ速度映射\n\n**需要修改两处**：\n\n1. **PTZManager.ptz_move** (第2375行)：直接传 `speed`，不要做 `/100.0` 映射\n   ```python\n   # 当前（错误）：\n   pan = int(round(pan_val * speed / 100.0))  # speed=100 → pan=1\n   \n   # 修复（正确）：\n   pan = pan_val * speed  # speed=100 → pan=100\n   ```\n\n2. **PTZController.continuous_move** (第1222行)：直接传值，不要做 `/10.0` 映射\n   ```python\n   # 当前（错误）：\n   pan_speed = round(pan / 10.0)  # pan=1 → 0\n   \n   # 修复（正确）：\n   pan_speed = int(pan)  # 直接传值\n   ```\n\n让我现在开始修复："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-12335ea6236c46308f5b0aaf5daee64b","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":30,"offset":1218,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\core\\ptz_manager.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":41860,"output":660,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42520,"cost":{"input":0.04186,"output":0.002112,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.043972000000000004}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781382351895,"responseId":"cht000ddf90@dx19ec2a991a0b894142"}}
{"type":"message","id":"8dff7941","parentId":"e4078a5a","timestamp":"2026-06-13T20:26:07.648Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-12335ea6236c46308f5b0aaf5daee64b","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    def focus_move_continuous(self, direction: str, speed: int = 50) -> bool:\r\n        \"\"\"连续对焦移动 - 通过官方 Focus 端点。\r\n\r\n        direction: 'near' (前移/近焦) 或 'far' (后移/远焦)\r\n        speed: 用户输入 1-100，但官方界面使用固定值 60\r\n        \r\n        官方界面: 点击聚焦按钮时发送 focus=±60\r\n        \"\"\"\r\n        endpoint = f\"/System/Video/inputs/channels/{self.channel}/focus\"\r\n        \r\n        # 官方界面使用固定值 60，忽略用户 speed 输入\r\n        focus_speed = 60\r\n        \r\n        if direction == 'near':\r\n            focus_speed = -focus_speed\r\n        \r\n        xml = f'''<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\r\n<FocusData>\r\n  <focus>{focus_speed}</focus>\r\n</FocusData>'''\r\n        \r\n        result = self.client.put(endpoint, xml)\r\n        return result.status_code == 200\r\n\r\n    def focus_stop(self) -> bool:\r\n        \"\"\"停止对焦移动。\"\"\"\r\n        endpoint = f\"/System/Video/inputs/channels/{self.channel}/focus\"\r\n        xml = '''<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\r\n<FocusData>\r\n  <focus>0</focus>\r\n\n[1661 more lines in file. Use offset=1248 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781382367648}}
