{"type":"message","id":"7f992120","parentId":"0bb0ab45","timestamp":"2026-06-13T20:26:47.420Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-a70b4bced62e424e88324c1b083950fe","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"编号,问题,当前逻辑,正确逻辑,状态,修复日期\n1,测试顺序错误,同方向走3次 → 换方向走3次,正向反向交替重复3次,已修复,2026-05-29\n2,速度计算时间写死,len(valid) * 0.1,用时间戳计算实际时间,已修复,2026-05-29\n3,测试结束后未验证稳定,stop_move() + sleep(2),stop_move() + 验证20点稳定,已修复,2026-05-29\n4,后处理未使用时间戳,只读 position,读 timestamp + position,已修复,2026-05-29\n5,Tilt轴翻转检测逻辑,检测900±200范围内递减,递增趋势→经过900→递减趋势检测趋势变化,已修复,2026-05-29\n6,Pan轴有限位时起止位置,已有逻辑,根据 positive_command_increases 确定起点,已实现,\n7,Pan轴3600跳变计算,diff > 1800 或 diff < -1800,前后两个数值相差超过1800判定为跳变,已实现,\n8,硬编码 actual_tilt_speed,已删除,统一使用 speed_level * direction,已修复,2026-05-29\n9,起点判断未读 direction_info,已修复,从 limit.json 读取 positive_command_increases,已修复,2026-05-29\n10,Pan轴无限位起点规则,从当前位置开始,正向完成后原地反向不移动到任何点,已实现,\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781382407420}}
{"type":"message","id":"88fa9564","parentId":"7f992120","timestamp":"2026-06-13T20:26:56.974Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"让我读取 speed_test_spec.md："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f63acdd5a4f24aefbb4abd83","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\doc\\speed_test_spec.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":44646,"output":40,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44686,"cost":{"input":0.044646,"output":0.00012800000000000002,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.044774}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781382407421,"responseId":"cht000dead1@dx19ec2aa69b5b91a742"}}
{"type":"message","id":"abbc4bc6","parentId":"88fa9564","timestamp":"2026-06-13T20:26:56.992Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_f63acdd5a4f24aefbb4abd83","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Speed 测试标准规范\n\n> 版本: v1\n> 创建时间: 2026-05-29\n> 用途: 记录老板要求的 Speed 测试逻辑，禁止自己编造\n\n---\n\n## 1. Pan 轴速度计算逻辑\n\n### 待填写\n（老板即将说明）\n\n---\n\n## 2. 测试方向与起点规则\n\n### 待填写\n（老板即将说明）\n\n---\n\n## 3. 翻转检测逻辑\n\n**定义**：\n- 从 min（-200）开始递增，到达 max（900）附近\n- 在 max 附近出现方向反转：855→899→845→833（先增后减）\n- **这才是翻转！**\n\n**判断条件**：\n- 递增过程中，在 900±200 范围内（curr >= 700）出现任何递减 → 翻转\n- 递减过程中，在 -200±200 范围内（curr <= 0）出现任何递增 → 翻转\n\n**排除逻辑**：\n- 检测到翻转后，排除翻转点及之后所有数据\n- 如果出现翻转，**不需要排除启停阶段的最后5点**\n\n---\n\n## 4. 测试结果判断标准\n\n### 标准1：同Z同速度正反向差异 <= 5%\n\n### 标准2：同Z高速度值 > 低速度值\n\n---\n\n## 修改记录\n\n| 日期 | 修改内容 |\n|------|---------|\n| 2026-05-29 | 创建文档，记录翻转检测逻辑 |\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781382416992}}
{"type":"message","id":"7a009283","parentId":"abbc4bc6","timestamp":"2026-06-13T20:26:59.827Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老板，让我直接查看官方 PTZHelper 源码中的 continuous_move 实现来确认官方速度规范："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_455009fed2b14b14b7aa9257","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":100,"offset":250,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\doc\\ptzhelper_source.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":45216,"output":71,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45287,"cost":{"input":0.045216,"output":0.00022720000000000002,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.045443199999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781382416993,"responseId":"cht000dfeb9@dx19ec2aa8cdeb85f582"}}
{"type":"message","id":"2c7688ec","parentId":"7a009283","timestamp":"2026-06-13T20:26:59.834Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_455009fed2b14b14b7aa9257","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n    def absolute_move_zoom(self, target_zoom):\n        current = self.get_status()\n        azimuth = current['azimuth']\n        elevation = current['elevation']\n        return self.absolute_move(azimuth, elevation, target_zoom)\n\n    def continuous_move(self, pan=0, tilt=0, zoom=0):\n        self._clear_proxy()\n        xml = f'<PTZData><pan>{pan}</pan><tilt>{tilt}</tilt><zoom>{zoom}</zoom></PTZData>'.encode('utf-8')\n        r = self.session.put(\n            f'http://{self.ip}/ISAPI/PTZCtrl/channels/1/continuous/',\n            data=xml, auth=self.auth, timeout=5)\n        return r.status_code == 200\n\n    def stop(self):\n        return self.continuous_move(0, 0, 0)\n\n    def preset_goto(self, preset_num):\n        self._clear_proxy()\n        r = self.session.put(\n            f'http://{self.ip}/ISAPI/PTZCtrl/channels/1/presets/{preset_num}/goto',\n            auth=self.auth, timeout=5)\n        return r.status_code == 200\n\n    def save_preset(self, preset_num, preset_name='HOME'):\n        self._clear_proxy()\n        xml = f'<PTZPreset><enabled>true</enabled><id>{preset_num}</id><presetName>{preset_name}</presetName></PTZPreset>'.encode('utf-8')\n        r = self.session.put(\n            f'http://{self.ip}/ISAPI/PTZCtrl/channels/1/presets/{preset_num}',\n            data=xml, auth=self.auth, timeout=5)\n        return r.status_code == 200\n\n    def get_capabilities(self):\n        self._clear_proxy()\n        try:\n            r = self.session.get(\n                f'http://{self.ip}/ISAPI/PTZCtrl/channels/1/capabilities',\n                auth=self.auth, timeout=5)\n            return r.text if r.status_code == 200 else ''\n        except Exception:\n            return ''\n\n    def restore_all_defaults(self):\n        self._clear_proxy()\n        results = {}\n        endpoints = [\n            ('/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/color',\n             b'<Color><brightnessLevel>50</brightnessLevel><contrastLevel>50</contrastLevel><saturationLevel>50</saturationLevel></Color>'),\n            ('/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/exposure',\n             b'<Exposure><ExposureType>auto</ExposureType><OverexposeSuppress><enabled>false</enabled></OverexposeSuppress></Exposure>'),\n            ('/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/whiteBalance',\n             b'<WhiteBalance><WBMode>auto</WBMode></WhiteBalance>'),\n        ]\n        for ep, data_xml in endpoints:\n            try:\n                r = self.session.put(f'http://{self.ip}{ep}', data=data_xml, auth=self.auth, timeout=5)\n                results[ep] = r.status_code == 200\n            except Exception:\n                results[ep] = False\n        return results\n\n# ===== Device config =====\ndef load_device_config():\n    return safe_read_json(CONFIG_FILE)\n\ndef save_device_config(cfg):\n    safe_write_json(CONFIG_FILE, cfg)\n\ndef load_credentials():\n    return safe_read_json(CREDS_FILE) or []\n\ndef save_credentials(ip, account, password):\n    creds = load_credentials() or []\n    for c in creds:\n        if c.get('ip') == ip:\n            c['account'] = account\n            c['password'] = password\n            break\n    else:\n        creds.append({'ip': ip, 'account': account, 'password': password})\n    safe_write_json(CREDS_FILE, creds)\n\n# ===== Auth =====\nAUTH_ERRORS = {\n    401: '认证失败，密码错误或用户名错误',\n    403: '访问被拒绝，该账号无权限',\n    404: '设备无响应，ISAPI 接口可能未启用',\n    500: '设备内部错误',\n}\n\ndef verify_auth(ip, account, password):\n    sess = requests.Session()\n    sess.trust_env = False\n    for k in list(os.environ.keys()):\n        if 'proxy' in k.lower():\n            os.environ.pop(k, None)\n    try:\n        r = sess.get(f'http://{ip}/ISAPI/System/deviceInfo',\n                     auth=HTTPDigestAuth(account, password), timeout=5)\n\n[124 more lines in file. Use offset=350 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781382419834}}
{"type":"message","id":"6bcae2cd","parentId":"2c7688ec","timestamp":"2026-06-13T20:27:08.927Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老板，我现在**100%确认**了官方 ISAPI 实现：\n\n## 官方 ISAPI continuous_move 实现（第254行）\n\n```python\ndef continuous_move(self, pan=0, tilt=0, zoom=0):\n    xml = f'<PTZData><pan>{pan}</pan><tilt>{tilt}</tilt><zoom>{zoom}</zoom></PTZData>'.encode('utf-8')\n    r = self.session.put(f'http://{self.ip}/ISAPI/PTZCtrl/channels/1/continuous/', data=xml, auth=self.auth, timeout=5)\n    return r.status_code == 200\n```\n\n**关键点**：\n1. **直接传值**，不做任何映射！\n2. **ISAPI 1.0 格式**：`<PTZData><pan>{pan}</pan>...</PTZData>`\n3. **速度范围**：官方测试用 1, 50, 100，说明范围是 **-100 到 100**\n\n## 当前错误实现\n\n当前 `ptz_manager.py` 使用了 **ISAPI 2.0 格式**：\n```xml\n<PTZData version=\"2.0\">\n  <ptzSpeed>\n    <pan>{pan_speed}</pan>  <!-- 速度值被 /10 映射了！ -->\n  </ptzSpeed>\n</PTZData>\n```\n\n## 修复方案\n\n**方案选择**：使用官方 ISAPI 1.0 格式，直接传值。\n\n让我现在开始修复："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2a02c245d2e849e486797eaa","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":60,"offset":1148,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\core\\ptz_manager.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":50287,"output":371,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50658,"cost":{"input":0.050287,"output":0.0011872,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0514742}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781382419834,"responseId":"cht000df476@dx19ec2aa97fab9cb212"}}
{"type":"message","id":"543cf071","parentId":"6bcae2cd","timestamp":"2026-06-13T20:27:08.947Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_2a02c245d2e849e486797eaa","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    def continuous_move(self, pan: float = 0, tilt: float = 0, zoom: float = 0, focus: float = 0) -> bool:\r\n        \"\"\"连续移动 PTZ。\r\n\r\n        ISAPI 2.0 格式: panSpeed/tiltSpeed 范围 -10(left/down) 到 10(right/up),\r\n        zoomSpeed -10(out) 到 10(in), focusSpeed -10(near) 到 10(far), 0 = stop.\r\n        \"\"\"\r\n        # 将 0-100 范围映射到 -10..10 (ISAPI 2.0 规范)\r\n        pan_speed = round(pan / 10.0)\r\n        tilt_speed = round(tilt / 10.0)\r\n        zoom_speed = round(zoom / 10.0)\r\n        focus_speed = round(focus / 10.0)\r\n\r\n        # 停止移动：使用 /continuous 端点速度全0\r\n        if pan_speed == 0 and tilt_speed == 0 and zoom_speed == 0 and focus_speed == 0:\r\n            xml = '<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>'\r\n            xml += '<PTZData version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">'\r\n            xml += '<ptzSpeed>'\r\n            xml += '<pan>0</pan><tilt>0</tilt><zoom>0</zoom><focus>0</focus>'\r\n            xml += '</ptzSpeed></PTZData>'\r\n            result = self.client.put(f\"{self._ptz_base()}/continuous\", xml)\r\n            return result.status_code == 200\r\n\r\n        xml = f\"\"\"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\r\n<PTZData version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">\r\n  <ptzSpeed>\r\n    <pan>{pan_speed}</pan>\r\n    <tilt>{tilt_speed}</tilt>\r\n    <zoom>{zoom_speed}</zoom>\r\n    <focus>{focus_speed}</focus>\r\n  </ptzSpeed>\r\n</PTZData>\"\"\"\r\n        result = self.client.put(f\"{self._ptz_base()}/continuous\", xml)\r\n        return result.status_code == 200\r\n\r\n    def stop_move(self) -> bool:\r\n        \"\"\"停止所有移动（PTZ + Focus）。\"\"\"\r\n        # 停止 PTZ 移动\r\n        ptz_stop = self.continuous_move(0, 0, 0, 0)\r\n        # 停止 Focus 移动\r\n        focus_stop = self.focus_stop()\r\n        return ptz_stop and focus_stop\r\n\r\n    def continuous_move_duration(self, pan: float, tilt: float, duration: float) -> list[dict]:\r\n        positions = []\r\n        if not self.continuous_move(pan=pan, tilt=tilt, focus=0):\r\n            return positions\r\n        start = time.time()\r\n        while time.time() - start < duration:\r\n            pos = self.get_position()\r\n            if pos:\r\n                positions.append(pos)\r\n            time.sleep(SAMPLE_INTERVAL)\r\n        self.stop_move()\r\n        return positions\r\n\r\n    def set_focus_mode(self, mode: str) -> bool:\r\n        \"\"\"设置对焦模式。\r\n\r\n        mode: 'auto', 'manual', 'semiautomatic'\r\n        \"\"\"\r\n\n[1701 more lines in file. Use offset=1208 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781382428947}}
