{"type":"message","id":"97573476","parentId":"8f06a0f6","timestamp":"2026-06-13T20:34:56.651Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老板，我找到了关键信息！从设备 capabilities 返回：\n\n```xml\n<ContinuousPanTiltSpace>\n  <XRange>\n    <Min>-100</Min>\n    <Max>100</Max>\n  </XRange>\n  <YRange>\n    <Min>-100</Min>\n    <Max>100</Max>\n  </YRange>\n</ContinuousPanTiltSpace>\n```\n\n**官方 ISAPI continuous_move 速度范围是 -100 到 100**，不是 1-7 档！\n\n这说明我之前的修复是正确的：直接传 -100 到 100 的速度值。\n\n但老板您说官方 web 端是 1-7 档，让我查看官方 web 端是如何处理速度的。可能是 web 界面将 1-7 档映射到 ISAPI 的速度值。\n\n让我查找海康威视官方的速度档位映射："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7116681ac77144d8867f948c","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd astrohub; python -c \"\nimport os\nos.environ.pop('http_proxy', None)\nos.environ.pop('https_proxy', None)\nimport requests\nfrom requests.auth import HTTPDigestAuth\nr = requests.get('http://192.168.5.72/ISAPI/Image/channels/1', auth=HTTPDigestAuth('admin', 'Nftw1357'), timeout=15, proxies={'http':None,'https':None})\nprint(r.text if r.status_code==200 else f'Error: {r.status_code}')\n\" 2>&1 | Select-Object -First 100","timeout":20,"workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":89431,"output":350,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":89781,"cost":{"input":0.089431,"output":0.0011200000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.09055099999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781382885279,"responseId":"cht000d36b9@dx19ec2b1b923ba5a412"}}
