{"type":"message","id":"9da30039","parentId":"8ffa6c54","timestamp":"2026-06-13T20:35:18.185Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_041b4d25e4c04b19b77687a5","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"编号,问题,当前逻辑,正确逻辑,状态,修复日期\n1,测试顺序错误,同方向走3次 → 换方向走3次,正向反向交替重复3次,已修复,2026-05-29\n2,速度计算时间写死,len(valid) * 0.1,用时间戳计算实际时间,已修复,2026-05-29\n3,测试结束后未验证稳定,stop_move() + sleep(2),stop_move() + 验证20点稳定,已修复,2026-05-29\n4,后处理未使用时间戳,只读 position,读 timestamp + position,已修复,2026-05-29\n5,Tilt轴翻转检测逻辑,检测900±200范围内递减,递增趋势→经过900→递减趋势检测趋势变化,已修复,2026-05-29\n6,Pan轴有限位时起止位置,已有逻辑,根据 positive_command_increases 确定起点,已实现,\n7,Pan轴3600跳变计算,diff > 1800 或 diff < -1800,前后两个数值相差超过1800判定为跳变,已实现,\n8,硬编码 actual_tilt_speed,已删除,统一使用 speed_level * direction,已修复,2026-05-29\n9,起点判断未读 direction_info,已修复,从 limit.json 读取 positive_command_increases,已修复,2026-05-29\n10,Pan轴无限位起点规则,从当前位置开始,正向完成后原地反向不移动到任何点,已实现,\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781382918185}}
{"type":"message","id":"57676492","parentId":"9da30039","timestamp":"2026-06-13T20:35:29.998Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老板，我看到 `speed_level` 这个词。让我查找 speed.py 中的速度档位定义："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_02fe26a303a44b19a13ce047","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":100,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\advanced\\speed.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":91298,"output":60,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":91358,"cost":{"input":0.09129799999999999,"output":0.000192,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.09148999999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781382918187,"responseId":"cht000d6b2b@dx19ec2b24e3fb958232"}}
{"type":"message","id":"a6fc6bf3","parentId":"57676492","timestamp":"2026-06-13T20:35:30.005Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_02fe26a303a44b19a13ce047","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"\"\"\r\nAstroHub v2.0 - 速度测试模块 (Speed Testing)\r\n\r\n实现速度测试:\r\n- measure_speed_single: 单点速度测量\r\n- post_process_csv: 数据后处理\r\n- run_all_tests: 完整测试流程\r\n\r\nAuthor: 雅痞张@南方天文\r\n\"\"\"\r\n\r\nfrom __future__ import annotations\r\n\r\nimport csv\r\nimport time\r\nfrom datetime import datetime\r\nfrom pathlib import Path\r\nfrom typing import Any\r\n\r\nfrom src.advanced.device_path import get_device_info, get_data_path_read, get_data_path_write, get_devices_dir\r\n\r\ndef _print(msg: str = \"\", end: str = \"\\n\"):\r\n    \"\"\"静默可控的print。\"\"\"\r\n    import src.ptz.core.logger as logger_module\r\n    if not getattr(logger_module.LOG, 'silent', False):\r\n        print(msg, end=end)\r\n\r\nSPEED_PROFILES = {\r\n    'lite': [1, 50, 100],\r\n    'medium': [round(1 + i * (100 - 1) / 7) for i in range(8)],  # 1-100 7等分\r\n    'full': [round(1 + i * (100 - 1) / 25) for i in range(26)],  # 1-100 25等分\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\ndef load_limit_data(model_short: str, mac_clean: str) -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"从limit.json读取限位数据。\r\n\r\n    Args:\r\n        model_short: 短型号\r\n        mac_clean: MAC地址(无冒号,小写)\r\n\r\n    Returns:\r\n        dict: 限位数据\r\n    \"\"\"\r\n    import json\r\n    limit_path = get_data_path_read(model_short, mac_clean, 'limit')\r\n    if limit_path is None or not limit_path.exists():\r\n        raise FileNotFoundError(\"limit.json不存在\")\r\n    with open(limit_path, \"r\", encoding=\"utf-8\") as f:\r\n        return json.load(f)\r\n\r\n# Pan轴是360度循环,3600=0\r\n# 所以测试Pan轴时,不要使用3600作为起点,使用0或接近0的值\r\n\r\n\r\ndef measure_speed_single(ptz: Any, axis: str, speed_level: int, raw_csv_path: str,\r\n                         direction: int = 1, zoom_val: int = 10, repeat_idx: int = 0,\r\n                         start_position: float | None = None,\r\n                         limit_data: dict | None = None) -> list[float]:\r\n    \"\"\"测量单轴单速度点的位移。\r\n\r\n    Args:\r\n        ptz: PTZController实例\r\n        axis: 轴名称\r\n        speed_level: 速度等级\r\n        raw_csv_path: CSV路径\r\n        direction: 方向 (1=正向, -1=负向)\r\n        zoom_val: Zoom档位\r\n        repeat_idx: 重复索引\r\n        start_position: 起始位置(绝对移动目标)\r\n        limit_data: 限位数据(从limit.json读取)\r\n        actual_tilt_speed: Tilt轴实际运动速度(正负值,从run_all_tests传入)\r\n\r\n    Returns:\r\n        list[float]: 采样点\r\n    \"\"\"\r\n    # 从limit_data读取限位值\r\n    if limit_data is None:\r\n        raise ValueError(\"limit_data不能为空,必须从limit.json读取\")\r\n\r\n    tilt_min = limit_data.get(\"tilt_min\", -200)\r\n    tilt_max = limit_data.get(\"tilt_max\", 900)\r\n    has_flip = limit_data.get(\"has_flip\", False)\r\n    is_infinite = limit_data.get(\"is_infinite\", True)\r\n    pan_min = limit_data.get(\"pan_min\", 0)\r\n    pan_max = limit_data.get(\"pan_max\", 3600)\r\n\r\n    # 所有移动开始前必须判断稳定\r\n    # Pan无限位:从当前位置开始,要求稳定\r\n    # Pan有限位/Tilt:绝对移动到起点,验证稳定\r\n    if start_position is not None:\r\n        # 绝对移动到起点\r\n        ptz.absolute_move(\r\n            pan=int(start_position) if axis == \"pan\" else 1800,\r\n            tilt=int(start_position) if axis == \"tilt\" else 450,\r\n            zoom=zoom_val,\r\n            speed=50\r\n        )\r\n        # 验证稳定:连续20点绝对相等\r\n        stable_count = 0\r\n\n[611 more lines in file. Use offset=101 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781382930005}}
{"type":"message","id":"450498cc","parentId":"a6fc6bf3","timestamp":"2026-06-13T20:35:45.278Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老板，我找到了！`SPEED_PROFILES` 定义了速度档位：\n\n```python\nSPEED_PROFILES = {\n    'lite': [1, 50, 100],\n    'medium': [round(1 + i * (100 - 1) / 7) for i in range(8)],  # 1-100 7等分\n    'full': [round(1 + i * (100 - 1) / 25) for i in range(26)],  # 1-100 25等分\n}\n```\n\n**medium 模式就是 8 档（0-7）**：`[1, 15, 29, 43, 57, 71, 85, 100]`\n\n但是老板，官方 web 端的速度控制方式可能不同。让我直接查看海康威视官方 web 界面的 PTZ 控制实现。您能告诉我官方 web 端的 PTZ 速度控制是什么样的吗？\n\n现在让我先完成其他修复任务：\n\n## 当前修复进度\n\n1. ✅ **PTZ速度修复** - 已修复 `continuous_move` 和 `ptz_move`，直接传 -100 到 100\n2. ⏳ **画面控制端点检查**\n3. ⏳ **画面控制登录复用检查**\n4. ⏳ **重置按钮实现**\n\n让我继续检查画面控制端点："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f38cbe524c4b46b1b30d8959","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Select-String -Path \"astrohub\\src\\api\\router.py\" -Pattern \"whiteBalance|Shutter|Iris|noiseReduce|Sharpness|color\" -Context 0,3 | Select-Object -First 30","workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":92469,"output":382,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":92851,"cost":{"input":0.092469,"output":0.0012224,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0936914}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781382930007,"responseId":"cht000d54af@dx19ec2b26ef6ba5b442"}}
