{"type":"message","id":"97ba52b4","parentId":"9d2ca62e","timestamp":"2026-06-13T20:35:56.649Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老板，我看到画面控制端点已经实现了。现在让我检查画面控制是否正确复用登录凭据。让我查找画面控制 API 获取客户端的方式："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b4f0d6e1cc834f54a50f3693","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":100,"offset":2610,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\api\\router.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":95929,"output":80,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":96009,"cost":{"input":0.095929,"output":0.00025600000000000004,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.096185}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781382945841,"responseId":"cht000d5209@dx19ec2b2b3fdb8ab282"}}
{"type":"message","id":"fa5e10ab","parentId":"97ba52b4","timestamp":"2026-06-13T20:35:56.660Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_b4f0d6e1cc834f54a50f3693","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\r\n\r\n@api_router.get(\"/ptz/{device_id}/image/whitebalance\", summary=\"获取白平衡设置\", tags=[\"Image\"])\r\nasync def get_whitebalance(device_id: str) -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"获取设备白平衡当前设置。\"\"\"\r\n    import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\r\n    mgr: PTZManager | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_manager\")\r\n    if not mgr:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"PTZManager 未初始化\"}\r\n\r\n    target_ip = _resolve_device_id_to_ip(mgr, device_id)\r\n    if not target_ip:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"无法解析设备标识: {device_id}\"}\r\n\r\n    ctrl, err = mgr._get_controller(target_ip)\r\n    if err:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": err}\r\n\r\n    client = ctrl.client\r\n    try:\r\n        resp = client.get(\"/Image/channels/1/whiteBalance\")\r\n        if resp.status_code != 200:\r\n            return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"获取白平衡失败: HTTP {resp.status_code}\"}\r\n\r\n        root = ET.fromstring(resp.xml)\r\n        result = {\"success\": True, \"data\": {}}\r\n        for elem in root.iter():\r\n            tag = elem.tag.split(\"}\")[-1] if \"}\" in elem.tag else elem.tag\r\n            if tag == \"WhiteBalanceStyle\":\r\n                result[\"data\"][\"mode\"] = (elem.text or \"manual\").lower()\r\n            elif tag == \"WhiteBalanceRed\":\r\n                result[\"data\"][\"red_gain\"] = int((elem.text or \"50\").strip())\r\n            elif tag == \"WhiteBalanceBlue\":\r\n                result[\"data\"][\"blue_gain\"] = int((elem.text or \"50\").strip())\r\n            elif tag == \"whiteBalanceRed\":\r\n                result[\"data\"][\"red_gain\"] = int((elem.text or \"50\").strip())\r\n            elif tag == \"whiteBalanceBlue\":\r\n                result[\"data\"][\"blue_gain\"] = int((elem.text or \"50\").strip())\r\n\r\n        result[\"data\"][\"min\"] = 0\r\n        result[\"data\"][\"max\"] = 255\r\n        result[\"data\"][\"supported_modes\"] = [\"manual\", \"auto\"]\r\n        return result\r\n    except Exception as e:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"获取白平衡异常: {e}\"}\r\n\r\n\r\n@api_router.post(\"/ptz/{device_id}/image/whitebalance\", summary=\"设置白平衡\", tags=[\"Image\"])\r\nasync def set_whitebalance(device_id: str, data: dict) -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"设置白平衡参数（模式或R/B增益）。\"\"\"\r\n    import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\r\n    mgr: PTZManager | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_manager\")\r\n    if not mgr:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"PTZManager 未初始化\"}\r\n\r\n    target_ip = _resolve_device_id_to_ip(mgr, device_id)\r\n    if not target_ip:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"无法解析设备标识: {device_id}\"}\r\n\r\n    ctrl, err = mgr._get_controller(target_ip)\r\n    if err:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": err}\r\n\r\n    client = ctrl.client\r\n    try:\r\n        # 直接构造 XML\r\n        mode_val = data.get(\"mode\", \"auto\")  # 小写！\r\n        red_val = data.get(\"red_gain\", 50)\r\n        blue_val = data.get(\"blue_gain\", 50)\r\n        \r\n        # 获取当前值\r\n        resp = client.get(\"/Image/channels/1/whiteBalance\")\r\n        if resp.status_code == 200:\r\n            import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\r\n            root = ET.fromstring(resp.xml)\r\n            for elem in root.iter():\r\n                tag = elem.tag.split(\"}\")[-1] if \"}\" in elem.tag else elem.tag\r\n                if tag == \"WhiteBalanceRed\":\r\n                    red_val = int(elem.text or 50)\r\n                elif tag == \"WhiteBalanceBlue\":\r\n                    blue_val = int(elem.text or 50)\r\n        \r\n        xml_str = f'''<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\r\n<WhiteBalance version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">\r\n<WhiteBalanceStyle>{mode_val}</WhiteBalanceStyle>\r\n<WhiteBalanceRed>{red_val}</WhiteBalanceRed>\r\n<WhiteBalanceBlue>{blue_val}</WhiteBalanceBlue>\r\n</WhiteBalance>'''\r\n        \r\n        put_resp = client.put(\"/Image/channels/1/whiteBalance\", xml_str)\r\n        if put_resp.status_code == 200:\r\n            return {\"success\": True, \"message\": \"白平衡已更新\"}\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"更新失败: HTTP {put_resp.status_code}\"}\r\n    except Exception as e:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"设置白平衡异常: {e}\"}\r\n\r\n\r\n@api_router.get(\"/ptz/{device_id}/image/noisereduce\", summary=\"获取降噪设置\", tags=[\"Image\"])\r\nasync def get_noisereduce(device_id: str) -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"获取设备降噪当前设置。\"\"\"\r\n\n[531 more lines in file. Use offset=2710 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781382956660}}
{"type":"message","id":"5a67d32f","parentId":"fa5e10ab","timestamp":"2026-06-13T20:36:10.011Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老板，画面控制 API 通过 `mgr._get_controller(target_ip)` 获取控制器，然后使用 `ctrl.client` 发送请求。这意味着画面控制**复用了 PTZ 控制的登录凭据**，这是正确的。\n\n现在让我更新 HEARTBEAT.md 并运行端到端测试："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_48c098b6a9304bbfb94b9b75","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 心跳与任务状态\n\n**最后更新**: 2026-06-14 04:40\n**状态**: v6.46 PTZ速度修复完成\n**工作空间**: C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\n\n### v6.46 修复内容\n\n| # | 问题 | 修复 | 文件 |\n|---|------|------|------|\n| 1 | PTZ速度映射错误 | `continuous_move` 直接传值（-100到100），不做 `/10` 映射 | `src/core/ptz_manager.py` |\n| 2 | PTZ速度计算错误 | `ptz_move` 直接传 `speed` 值，不做 `/100` 映射 | `src/core/ptz_manager.py` |\n\n### 官方 ISAPI 规范确认\n\n从设备 capabilities 获取：\n```xml\n<ContinuousPanTiltSpace>\n  <XRange><Min>-100</Min><Max>100</Max></XRange>\n  <YRange><Min>-100</Min><Max>100</Max></YRange>\n</ContinuousPanTiltSpace>\n```\n**速度范围：-100 到 100**\n\n### 待处理\n\n| 问题 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| PTZ速度档位（1-7档）| 需确认官方web端实现方式 |\n| 画面控制端点检查 | 已确认复用登录凭据 |\n| 重置按钮功能 | 待实现 |\n\n### 备份位置\n- backup_20260614_042423/\n","path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\HEARTBEAT.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":97345,"output":434,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":97779,"cost":{"input":0.097345,"output":0.0013888000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0987338}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781382956661,"responseId":"cht000e499c@dx19ec2b2cc7fb893102"}}
