{"type":"message","id":"1e9d586c","parentId":"0ff22132","timestamp":"2026-06-13T20:41:09.161Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老板，我找到了重要信息！\n\n```xml\n<panMaxSpeed>400</panMaxSpeed>\n<tiltMaxSpeed>200</tiltMaxSpeed>\n<presetSpeed>4</presetSpeed>\n<autoPatrolSpeed>70</autoPatrolSpeed>\n<keyBoardControlSpeed>normal</keyBoardControlSpeed>\n```\n\n这说明设备的 **Pan 最大速度是 400 度/秒**，**Tilt 最大速度是 200 度/秒**。这与 ISAPI continuous_move 的 -100 到 100 速度范围不同！\n\n让我进一步研究官方速度档位。现在让我继续修复其他问题：\n\n## 问题2：画面控制端点检查\n\n让我检查画面控制的下拉菜单和滑动条是否正确实现："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f88a8b51b98f4573adcb609f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Select-String -Path \"astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html\" -Pattern \"ir_led|白平衡|快门|光圈|降噪|锐度|亮度|对比度|饱和度\" -Context 0,3 | Select-Object -First 30","workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":93746,"output":240,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":93986,"cost":{"input":0.093746,"output":0.000768,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.094514}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781383253961,"responseId":"cht000d89fc@dx19ec2b76b07b85e102"}}
