{"type":"message","id":"6cd3c57f","parentId":"fb75f1ce","timestamp":"2026-06-13T20:50:59.982Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老板，后端已修复。现在更新 HEARTBEAT.md："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-dbb98dc1ab464c19bbac25756e77b0ac","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 心跳与任务状态\n\n**最后更新**: 2026-06-14 04:55\n**状态**: v6.52 PTZ速度档位修复完成\n**工作空间**: C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\n\n### v6.52 修复内容\n\n| # | 问题 | 修复 | 文件 |\n|---|------|------|------|\n| 1 | PTZ速度档位 | 1-7档映射到ISAPI速度值 | `src/core/ptz_manager.py` |\n| 2 | API默认速度 | 默认档位4（不是50） | `src/api/router.py` |\n| 3 | 重置按钮 | 重置画面控制到默认值 | `src/api/router.py` |\n\n### PTZ速度档位映射\n\n官方 web 端：**1-7 档，默认 4 档**\n\n| 档位 | ISAPI速度值 | 实际速度 |\n|------|------------|---------|\n| 1 | 14 | 14% 最大速度 |\n| 2 | 28 | 28% |\n| 3 | 43 | 43% |\n| 4 | 57 | 57% (默认) |\n| 5 | 71 | 71% |\n| 6 | 86 | 86% |\n| 7 | 100 | 100% 最大速度 |\n\n设备参数：\n- `panMaxSpeed`: 400 度/秒\n- `tiltMaxSpeed`: 200 度/秒\n\n### 备份位置\n- backup_20260614_042423/","path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\HEARTBEAT.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":100491,"output":401,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":100892,"cost":{"input":0.100491,"output":0.0012832000000000002,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1017742}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781383844520,"responseId":"cht000dec1e@dx19ec2c065a4ba5a412"}}
