{"type":"message","id":"22f6bc35","parentId":"912ac3b5","timestamp":"2026-06-13T20:51:09.651Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老板，修复完成！\n\n## 修复总结\n\n### PTZ 速度档位\n- **官方档位**：1-7 档，默认 4 档\n- **映射规则**：\n  - 档位 1 → ISAPI 速度 14\n  - 档位 2 → ISAPI 速度 28\n  - 档位 3 → ISAPI 速度 43\n  - 档位 4 → ISAPI 速度 57（默认）\n  - 档位 5 → ISAPI 速度 71\n  - 档位 6 → ISAPI 速度 86\n  - 档位 7 → ISAPI 速度 100\n\n### 修改的文件\n1. `src/core/ptz_manager.py` - 档位映射逻辑\n2. `src/api/router.py` - 默认速度值改为 4\n\n需要我运行端到端测试验证吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":110510,"output":212,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":110722,"cost":{"input":0.11051,"output":0.0006784,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.11118839999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781383859999,"responseId":"cht000dfab3@dx19ec2c09d11b85e102"}}
{"type":"message","id":"8ceee7fa","parentId":"22f6bc35","timestamp":"2026-06-13T20:51:15.571Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:8447197723\",\n  \"message_id\": \"35113\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-06-14 04:50 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yixing Zhang (8447197723)\",\n  \"id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"name\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"username\": \"ZhangyixingTG\"\n}\n```\n\n官方的最快移动速度远高于你开发的astrohub，上下限是有问题的，重新给我查询ISAPI端点，到底是怎么实现的。你需要测试速度400、200这些刚才提到的值\n禁止打补丁，精确修复"}],"timestamp":1781383875566}}
{"type":"message","id":"4165192e","parentId":"8ceee7fa","timestamp":"2026-06-13T20:51:30.963Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老板，我明白了。让我直接查询 ISAPI 端点，测试官方的速度实现方式。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1ffc891c9ce849d7a8777fa8","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd astrohub; python -c \"\nimport os\nos.environ.pop('http_proxy', None)\nimport requests\nfrom requests.auth import HTTPDigestAuth\nimport time\n\nip = '192.168.5.72'\nauth = HTTPDigestAuth('admin', 'Nftw1357')\nbase = f'http://{ip}/ISAPI/PTZCtrl/channels/1'\n\n# 1. 获取当前位置\ndef get_position():\n    r = requests.get(f'{base}/status', auth=auth, timeout=10, proxies={'http':None,'https':None})\n    if r.status_code == 200:\n        import re\n        az = re.search(r'<azimuth>(\\d+)</azimuth>', r.text)\n        el = re.search(r'<elevation>(-?\\d+)</elevation>', r.text)\n        return {\n            'azimuth': int(az.group(1)) if az else 0,\n            'elevation': int(el.group(1)) if el else 0\n        }\n    return None\n\n# 2. 发送 continuous_move 命令\ndef continuous_move(pan, tilt):\n    xml = f'<PTZData><pan>{pan}</pan><tilt>{tilt}</tilt><zoom>0</zoom></PTZData>'.encode('utf-8')\n    r = requests.put(f'{base}/continuous/', data=xml, auth=auth, timeout=10, proxies={'http':None,'https':None})\n    return r.status_code == 200\n\n# 3. 测试不同速度值\nprint('=== PTZ continuous_move 速度测试 ===')\nprint()\n\n# 获取当前位置\npos = get_position()\nprint(f'当前位置: azimuth={pos[\\\"azimuth\\\"]}, elevation={pos[\\\"elevation\\\"]}')\n\n# 测试速度值 400, 200, 100, 50\ntest_speeds = [400, 200, 100, 50, 14]\n\nfor speed in test_speeds:\n    print(f'\\\\n测试速度值: {speed}')\n    \n    # 记录开始位置\n    start = get_position()\n    print(f'  开始: azimuth={start[\\\"azimuth\\\"]}')\n    \n    # 发送移动命令\n    result = continuous_move(pan=speed, tilt=0)\n    print(f'  命令发送: {\\\"成功\\\" if result else \\\"失败\\\"} (pan={speed})')\n    \n    # 移动 2 秒\n    time.sleep(2)\n    \n    # 停止\n    continuous_move(0, 0)\n    time.sleep(0.5)\n    \n    # 记录结束位置\n    end = get_position()\n    print(f'  结束: azimuth={end[\\\"azimuth\\\"]}')\n    \n    # 计算移动量\n    delta = abs(end['azimuth'] - start['azimuth'])\n    print(f'  移动量: {delta} (2秒内)')\n\nprint('\\\\n=== 测试完成 ===')\n\" 2>&1","timeout":60,"workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":110922,"output":701,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":111623,"cost":{"input":0.11092199999999999,"output":0.0022432000000000003,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1131652}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781383875571,"responseId":"cht000d650f@dx19ec2c0d05dba60352"}}
