{"type":"message","id":"a3ba7edd","parentId":"6922c4a0","timestamp":"2026-06-13T21:04:05.282Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老板，我明白了！\n\n**官方 ISAPI 速度值是 1-400（Pan）和 1-200（Tilt），不是 -100 到 100！**\n\n让我重新修复："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d50a11914f7d423b96db044a","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"        # Pan/Tilt operations - 官方 ISAPI 速度值\n        # 官方 web 端: 1-7 档，默认 4 档\n        # 设备配置: panMaxSpeed=400, tiltMaxSpeed=200\n        # 档位映射: 1→57, 2→114, 3→171, 4→228, 5→286, 6→343, 7→400 (Pan)\n        pan_val, tilt_val = self.DIRECTION_MAP[direction]\n        \n        # 将 1-7 档映射到官方 ISAPI 速度值\n        if 1 <= speed <= 7:\n            # Pan 速度映射 (panMaxSpeed=400)\n            pan_speed_mapping = {1: 57, 2: 114, 3: 171, 4: 228, 5: 286, 6: 343, 7: 400}\n            # Tilt 速度映射 (tiltMaxSpeed=200)\n            tilt_speed_mapping = {1: 29, 2: 57, 3: 86, 4: 114, 5: 143, 6: 171, 7: 200}\n            \n            pan = int(pan_val * pan_speed_mapping.get(speed, 228))\n            tilt = int(tilt_val * tilt_speed_mapping.get(speed, 114))\n        else:\n            # 兼容旧版：直接使用速度值\n            pan = int(pan_val * min(max(speed, 0), 400))\n            tilt = int(tilt_val * min(max(speed, 0), 200))\n\n        success = ctrl.continuous_move(pan=pan, tilt=tilt)","oldText":"        # Pan/Tilt operations - 官方档位映射\n        # 官方 web 端: 1-7 档，默认 4 档\n        # 档位映射: 1→14, 2→28, 3→43, 4→57, 5→71, 6→86, 7→100\n        # 参考: 设备 capabilities ContinuousPanTiltSpace 范围 -100 到 100\n        pan_val, tilt_val = self.DIRECTION_MAP[direction]\n        \n        # 将 1-7 档映射到 ISAPI 速度值\n        if 1 <= speed <= 7:\n            # 官方档位映射\n            speed_mapping = {1: 14, 2: 28, 3: 43, 4: 57, 5: 71, 6: 86, 7: 100}\n            isapi_speed = speed_mapping.get(speed, 57)  # 默认档位 4 → 57"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output"