{"type":"message","id":"68edf57e","parentId":"e4c91010","timestamp":"2026-06-13T21:04:41.183Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老板，我明白了！官方 ISAPI 的速度值范围是 **1-400**（Pan）和 **1-200**（Tilt），不是 1-100！\n\n测试结果证明了这一点：\n- **pan=400** → 移动 265度\n- **pan=100** → 移动 266度（被限制！）\n- **pan=50** → 移动 103度\n\n**问题根源**：continuous_move 的速度上限被错误地限制为 100，实际应该是 400！\n\n让我立即修复："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-8d8e424610054b319a73ba0fd4a24674","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":30,"offset":1148,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\core\\ptz_manager.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":105011,"output":163,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":105174,"cost":{"input":0.105011,"output":0.0005216,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.10553259999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781384673050,"responseId":"cht000d9c8d@dx19ec2ccf9dab9ca102"}}
{"type":"message","id":"6cf703f0","parentId":"68edf57e","timestamp":"2026-06-13T21:04:41.191Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-8d8e424610054b319a73ba0fd4a24674","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    def continuous_move(self, pan: float = 0, tilt: float = 0, zoom: float = 0, focus: float = 0) -> bool:\r\n        \"\"\"连续移动 PTZ。\r\n\r\n        官方 ISAPI 1.0 格式: pan/tilt/zoom 直接传速度值，范围 -100 到 100。\r\n        参考: doc/ptzhelper_source.py continuous_move() - 直接传值不做映射。\r\n        \"\"\"\r\n        # 官方 ISAPI 1.0 格式：直接传值，不做映射\r\n        pan_speed = int(pan)\r\n        tilt_speed = int(tilt)\r\n        zoom_speed = int(zoom)\r\n        focus_speed = int(focus)\r\n\r\n        # 官方格式：<PTZData><pan>{pan}</pan><tilt>{tilt}</tilt><zoom>{zoom}</zoom></PTZData>\r\n        xml = f'<PTZData><pan>{pan_speed}</pan><tilt>{tilt_speed}</tilt><zoom>{zoom_speed}</zoom></PTZData>'.encode('utf-8')\r\n        result = self.client.put(f\"{self._ptz_base()}/continuous\", xml)\r\n        return result.status_code == 200\r\n\r\n    def stop_move(self) -> bool:\r\n        \"\"\"停止所有移动（PTZ + Focus）。\"\"\"\r\n        # 停止 PTZ 移动\r\n        ptz_stop = self.continuous_move(0, 0, 0, 0)\r\n        # 停止 Focus 移动\r\n        focus_stop = self.focus_stop()\r\n        return ptz_stop and focus_stop\r\n\r\n    def continuous_move_duration(self, pan: float, tilt: float, duration: float) -> list[dict]:\r\n        positions = []\r\n        if not self.continuous_move(pan=pan, tilt=tilt, focus=0):\r\n            return positions\r\n        start = time.time()\r\n\n[1733 more lines in file. Use offset=1178 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781384681191}}
{"type":"message","id":"15a6d4dd","parentId":"6cf703f0","timestamp":"2026-06-13T21:04:58.291Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老板，`continuous_move` 方法是对的（直接传值），问题在于档位映射！\n\n**官方档位映射应该是**：\n- 档位 7 → pan=400（最快）\n- 档位 4 → pan=228（默认）\n- 档位 1 → pan=57（最慢）\n\n让我修复档位映射："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_13cb5aaf768b48139f3bd02d","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"        # Pan/Tilt operations - 官方档位映射\n        # 官方 web 端: 1-7 档，默认 4 档\n        # 官方 ISAPI 速度范围: Pan -400 到 400, Tilt -200 到 200\n        # 档位映射: 1→57, 2→114, 3→171, 4→228, 5→285, 6→342, 7→400\n        # 参考: 测试验证 pan=400 是最大速度, pan=100 被限制到相同速度\n        pan_val, tilt_val = self.DIRECTION_MAP[direction]\n        \n        # 将 1-7 档映射到 ISAPI 速度值\n        if 1 <= speed <= 7:\n            # 官方档位映射 (Pan 最大 400)\n            speed_mapping = {1: 57, 2: 114, 3: 171, 4: 228, 5: 285, 6: 342, 7: 400}\n            isapi_speed = speed_mapping.get(speed, 228)  # 默认档位 4 → 228\n        else:\n            # 兼容旧版：直接使用 0-400 值\n            isapi_speed = min(max(speed, 0), 400)\n        \n        pan = int(pan_val * isapi_speed)\n        tilt = int(tilt_val * isapi_speed * 0.5)  # Tilt 最大 200","oldText":"        # Pan/Tilt operations - 官方档位映射\n        # 官方 web 端: 1-7 档，默认 4 档\n        # 档位映射: 1→14, 2→28, 3→43, 4→57, 5→71, 6→86, 7→100\n        # 参考: 设备 capabilities ContinuousPanTiltSpace 范围 -100 到 100\n        pan_val, tilt_val = self.DIRECTION_MAP[direction]\n        \n        # 将 1-7 档映射到 ISAPI 速度值\n        if 1 <= speed <= 7:\n            # 官方档位映射\n            speed_mapping = {1: 14, 2: 28, 3: 43, 4: 57, 5: 71, 6: 86, 7: 100}\n            isapi_speed = speed_mapping.get(speed, 57)  # 默认档位 4 → 57\n        else:\n            # 兼容旧版：直接使用 0-100 值\n            isapi_speed = min(max(speed, 0), 100)\n        \n        pan = int(pan_val * isapi_speed)\n        tilt = int(tilt_val * isapi_speed)"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\core\\ptz_manager.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":115445,"output":777,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":116222,"cost":{"input":0.11544499999999999,"output":0.0024864,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.11793139999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781384681193,"responseId":"cht000daaeb@dx19ec2cd1831ba5e412"}}
