{"type":"message","id":"560a5309","parentId":"7821268e","timestamp":"2026-06-13T21:05:27.646Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"更新 HEARTBEAT.md："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d55542af10d14365a7338bd1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 心跳与任务状态\n\n**最后更新**: 2026-06-14 05:10\n**状态**: v6.53 PTZ速度范围修复\n**工作空间**: C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\n\n### v6.53 修复内容\n\n| # | 问题 | 修复 | 文件 |\n|---|------|------|------|\n| 1 | ISAPI速度范围错误 | Pan最大400，Tilt最大200（不是100） | `src/core/ptz_manager.py` |\n| 2 | 档位映射错误 | 1→57, 2→114, 3→171, 4→228, 5→285, 6→342, 7→400 | `src/core/ptz_manager.py` |\n\n### PTZ速度档位映射（修正）\n\n官方 web 端：**1-7 档，默认 4 档**\n\n| 档位 | ISAPI Pan速度 | 实际效果 |\n|------|--------------|---------|\n| 1 | 57 | 最慢 |\n| 2 | 114 | |\n| 3 | 171 | |\n| 4 | 228 | 默认 |\n| 5 | 285 | |\n| 6 | 342 | |\n| 7 | 400 | 最快 |\n\n### ISAPI 速度范围（实测验证）\n\n```\npan=400 → 移动265度/2秒 → 最快\npan=100 → 移动266度/2秒 → 被限制（上限400）\npan=50  → 移动103度/2秒\npan=14  → 移动14度/2秒\n```\n\n### 备份位置\n- backup_20260614_042423/","path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\HEARTBEAT.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":106945,"output":437,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":107382,"cost":{"input":0.106945,"output":0.0013984000000000002,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.10834339999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781384720820,"responseId":"cht000dfe87@dx19ec2cdb812ba5d322"}}
