{"type":"message","id":"2802c0ca","parentId":"a4c06621","timestamp":"2026-06-13T21:05:34.933Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老板，修复完成！\n\n## 修复内容\n\n**ISAPI 速度范围**：\n- **Pan**: -400 到 400（不是 -100 到 100）\n- **Tilt**: -200 到 200\n\n**官方档位映射**：\n| 档位 | ISAPI速度 |\n|------|----------|\n| 1 | 57 |\n| 2 | 114 |\n| 3 | 171 |\n| 4 | 228（默认）|\n| 5 | 285 |\n| 6 | 342 |\n| 7 | 400（最快）|\n\n现在档位 7 会发送 pan=400，与官方 web 端最快速度一致。\n\n需要我验证修复效果吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":107223,"output":153,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":107376,"cost":{"input":0.107223,"output":0.0004896000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1077126}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781384727665,"responseId":"cht000db920@dx19ec2cdcf5db958232"}}
{"type":"message","id":"9bec41fe","parentId":"2802c0ca","timestamp":"2026-06-13T21:10:12.618Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:8447197723\",\n  \"message_id\": \"35130\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-06-14 05:10 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yixing Zhang (8447197723)\",\n  \"id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"name\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"username\": \"ZhangyixingTG\"\n}\n```\n\n完整验证"}],"timestamp":1781385012614}}
{"type":"message","id":"a861ca2d","parentId":"9bec41fe","timestamp":"2026-06-13T21:10:32.166Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老板，开始完整验证。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0d183c8c377e4ff9b9b300f9","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"\"\"\"PTZ 速度档位完整验证测试\"\"\"\nimport os\nos.environ.pop('http_proxy', None)\nimport requests\nfrom requests.auth import HTTPDigestAuth\nimport time\nimport re\n\nip = '192.168.5.72'\nauth = HTTPDigestAuth('admin', 'Nftw1357')\nbase = f'http://{ip}/ISAPI/PTZCtrl/channels/1'\n\ndef get_position():\n    r = requests.get(f'{base}/status', auth=auth, timeout=10, proxies={'http':None,'https':None})\n    if r.status_code == 200:\n        az = re.search(r'<azimuth>(\\d+)</azimuth>', r.text)\n        return {'azimuth': int(az.group(1)) if az else 0}\n    return None\n\ndef continuous_move(pan, tilt=0):\n    xml = f'<PTZData><pan>{pan}</pan><tilt>{tilt}</tilt><zoom>0</zoom></PTZData>'.encode('utf-8')\n    r = requests.put(f'{base}/continuous/', data=xml, auth=auth, timeout=10, proxies={'http':None,'https':None})\n    return r.status_code == 200\n\ndef test_speed(speed_value, label):\n    \"\"\"测试指定速度值\"\"\"\n    print(f'\\n{label}: ISAPI pan={speed_value}')\n    \n    start = get_position()\n    result = continuous_move(pan=speed_value)\n    time.sleep(2)\n    continuous_move(0, 0)\n    time.sleep(0.5)\n    end = get_position()\n    \n    delta = abs(end['azimuth'] - start['azimuth'])\n    actual_speed = delta / 2  # 度/秒\n    print(f'  移动量: {delta}度, 实际速度: {actual_speed}度/秒')\n    return delta\n\nprint('='*60)\nprint('PTZ 速度档位完整验证')\nprint('='*60)\n\n# 1. 测试官方档位映射后的 ISAPI 速度值\nprint('\\n【测试1】官方档位对应的ISAPI速度值')\n\nspeed_mapping = {1: 57, 2: 114, 3: 171, 4: 228, 5: 285, 6: 342, 7: 400}\nresults = {}\n\nfor gear, isapi_speed in speed_mapping.items():\n    delta = test_speed(isapi_speed, f'档位{gear}')\n    results[gear] = {'isapi': isapi_speed, 'delta': delta}\n    time.sleep(1)\n\n# 2. 验证速度上限\nprint('\\n【测试2】验证速度上限')\ntest_speed(400, '最大速度 pan=400')\ntest_speed(500, '超限测试 pan=500')\n\n# 3. 汇总\nprint('\\n' + '='*60)\nprint('验证结果汇总')\nprint('='*60)\nprint(f'{\"档位\":<6} {\"ISAPI值\":<10} {\"2秒移动\":<12} {\"速度(度/秒)\"}')\nprint('-'*60)\nfor gear in sorted(results.keys()):\n    r = results[gear]\n    speed = r['delta'] / 2\n    print(f'{gear:<6} {r[\"isapi\"]:<10} {r[\"delta\"]:<12} {speed:.1f}')\n\nprint('\\n验证完成!')\n","path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\tests\\test_ptz_speed_verify.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":117418,"output":780,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":118198,"cost":{"input":0.117418,"output":0.0024960000000000004,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.11991399999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781385012619,"responseId":"cht000dd552@dx19ec2d2276eb894142"}}
