{"type":"message","id":"39c8ee75","parentId":"994e04ff","timestamp":"2026-06-13T21:11:13.413Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_75412511ac5640dfba3b5f13","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[31;1mC:\\Python\\Lib\\site-packages\\requests\\__init__.py:113: RequestsDependencyWarning: urllib3 (2.1.0) or chardet (7.2.0)/charset_normalizer (3.4.6) doesn't match a supported version![0m\r\n[31;1m  warnings.warn([0m\r\n============================================================\r\nPTZ �ٶȵ�λ������֤\r\n============================================================\r\n\r\n������1���ٷ���λ��Ӧ��ISAPI�ٶ�ֵ\r\n\r\n��λ1: ISAPI pan=57\r\n  �ƶ���: 128��, ʵ���ٶ�: 64.0��/��\r\n\r\n��λ2: ISAPI pan=114\r\n  �ƶ���: 264��, ʵ���ٶ�: 132.0��/��\r\n\r\n��λ3: ISAPI pan=171\r\n  �ƶ���: 267��, ʵ���ٶ�: 133.5��/��\r\n\r\n��λ4: ISAPI pan=228\r\n  �ƶ���: 263��, ʵ���ٶ�: 131.5��/��\r\n\r\n��λ5: ISAPI pan=285\r\n  �ƶ���: 3331��, ʵ���ٶ�: 1665.5��/��\r\n\r\n��λ6: ISAPI pan=342\r\n  �ƶ���: 267��, ʵ���ٶ�: 133.5��/��\r\n\r\n��λ7: ISAPI pan=400\r\n  �ƶ���: 267��, ʵ���ٶ�: 133.5��/��\r\n\r\n������2����֤�ٶ�����\r\n\r\n����ٶ� pan=400: ISAPI pan=400\r\n  �ƶ���: 266��, ʵ���ٶ�: 133.0��/��\r\n\r\n���޲��� pan=500: ISAPI pan=500\r\n  �ƶ���: 266��, ʵ���ٶ�: 133.0��/��\r\n\r\n============================================================\r\n��֤�������\r\n============================================================\r\n��λ     ISAPIֵ     2���ƶ�         �ٶ�(��/��)\r\n------------------------------------------------------------\r\n1      57         128          64.0\r\n2      114        264          132.0\r\n3      171        267          133.5\r\n4      228        263          131.5\r\n5      285        3331         1665.5\r\n6      342        267          133.5\r\n7      400        267          133.5\r\n\r\n��֤���!\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"ember-summit","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[31;1mC:\\Python\\Lib\\site-packages\\requests\\__init__.py:113: RequestsDependencyWarning: urllib3 (2.1.0) or chardet (7.2.0)/charset_normalizer (3.4.6) doesn't match a supported version![0m\r\n[31;1m  warnings.warn([0m\r\n============================================================\r\nPTZ �ٶȵ�λ������֤\r\n============================================================\r\n\r\n������1���ٷ���λ��Ӧ��ISAPI�ٶ�ֵ\r\n\r\n��λ1: ISAPI pan=57\r\n  �ƶ���: 128��, ʵ���ٶ�: 64.0��/��\r\n\r\n��λ2: ISAPI pan=114\r\n  �ƶ���: 264��, ʵ���ٶ�: 132.0��/��\r\n\r\n��λ3: ISAPI pan=171\r\n  �ƶ���: 267��, ʵ���ٶ�: 133.5��/��\r\n\r\n��λ4: ISAPI pan=228\r\n  �ƶ���: 263��, ʵ���ٶ�: 131.5��/��\r\n\r\n��λ5: ISAPI pan=285\r\n  �ƶ���: 3331��, ʵ���ٶ�: 1665.5��/��\r\n\r\n��λ6: ISAPI pan=342\r\n  �ƶ���: 267��, ʵ���ٶ�: 133.5��/��\r\n\r\n��λ7: ISAPI pan=400\r\n  �ƶ���: 267��, ʵ���ٶ�: 133.5��/��\r\n\r\n������2����֤�ٶ�����\r\n\r\n����ٶ� pan=400: ISAPI pan=400\r\n  �ƶ���: 266��, ʵ���ٶ�: 133.0��/��\r\n\r\n���޲��� pan=500: ISAPI pan=500\r\n  �ƶ���: 266��, ʵ���ٶ�: 133.0��/��\r\n\r\n============================================================\r\n��֤�������\r\n============================================================\r\n��λ     ISAPIֵ     2���ƶ�         �ٶ�(��/��)\r\n------------------------------------------------------------\r\n1      57         128          64.0\r\n2      114        264          132.0\r\n3      171        267          133.5\r\n4      228        263          131.5\r\n5      285        3331         1665.5\r\n6      342        267          133.5\r\n7      400        267          133.5\r\n\r\n��֤���!\r\n","name":"cd astrohub;"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1781385073413}}
{"type":"message","id":"e83c7c9e","parentId":"39c8ee75","timestamp":"2026-06-13T21:11:34.113Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老板，测试结果很奇怪！\n\n**档位5（pan=285）移动了 3331 度**，这不对！可能是设备碰到了限位或者发生了跳变。\n\n让我重新测试，更仔细地观察："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_17e47ca567934c5eaf362de9","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"\"\"\"PTZ 速度精确验证测试\"\"\"\nimport os\nos.environ.pop('http_proxy', None)\nimport requests\nfrom requests.auth import HTTPDigestAuth\nimport time\nimport re\n\nip = '192.168.5.72'\nauth = HTTPDigestAuth('admin', 'Nftw1357')\nbase = f'http://{ip}/ISAPI/PTZCtrl/channels/1'\n\ndef get_position():\n    r = requests.get(f'{base}/status', auth=auth, timeout=10, proxies={'http':None,'https':None})\n    if r.status_code == 200:\n        az = re.search(r'<azimuth>(\\d+)</azimuth>', r.text)\n        el = re.search(r'<elevation>(-?\\d+)</elevation>', r.text)\n        return {\n            'azimuth': int(az.group(1)) if az else 0,\n            'elevation': int(el.group(1)) if el else 0\n        }\n    return None\n\ndef continuous_move(pan, tilt=0):\n    xml = f'<PTZData><pan>{pan}</pan><tilt>{tilt}</tilt><zoom>0</zoom></PTZData>'.encode('utf-8')\n    r = requests.put(f'{base}/continuous/', data=xml, auth=auth, timeout=10, proxies={'http':None,'https':None})\n    return r.status_code == 200\n\ndef goto_home():\n    \"\"\"回到预置点10\"\"\"\n    r = requests.put(f'{base}/presets/10/goto', auth=auth, timeout=10, proxies={'http':None,'https':None})\n    time.sleep(3)\n    return r.status_code == 200\n\nprint('='*60)\nprint('PTZ 速度精确验证')\nprint('='*60)\n\n# 先回到HOME位置\nprint('\\n回到HOME位置...')\ngoto_home()\npos = get_position()\nprint(f'当前位置: azimuth={pos[\"azimuth\"]}, elevation={pos[\"elevation\"]}')\n\n# 测试关键速度值\ntest_cases = [\n    (50, '慢速'),\n    (100, '中速'),\n    (200, '快速'),\n    (400, '最快'),\n]\n\nprint('\\n开始测试...\\n')\n\nfor speed, label in test_cases:\n    print(f'【{label}】pan={speed}')\n    \n    # 回到HOME\n    goto_home()\n    time.sleep(1)\n    \n    start = get_position()\n    print(f'  开始位置: az={start[\"azimuth\"]}')\n    \n    # 移动\n    continuous_move(pan=speed)\n    time.sleep(2)\n    continuous_move(0, 0)\n    time.sleep(0.5)\n    \n    end = get_position()\n    print(f'  结束位置: az={end[\"azimuth\"]}')\n    \n    # 计算移动量（处理3600跳变）\n    delta = end['azimuth'] - start['azimuth']\n    if delta > 1800:\n        delta = delta - 3600\n    elif delta < -1800:\n        delta = delta + 3600\n    delta = abs(delta)\n    \n    actual_speed = delta / 2\n    print(f'  移动量: {delta}度, 速度: {actual_speed:.1f}度/秒')\n    print()\n\nprint('='*60)\nprint('验证完成')\nprint('='*60)\n","path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\tests\\test_ptz_speed_precise.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":119071,"output":811,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":119882,"cost":{"input":0.119071,"output":0.0025952,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1216662}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781385073417,"responseId":"cht000de6de@dx19ec2d31819b9cb212"}}
