{"type":"message","id":"070c0320","parentId":"c60c3aa6","timestamp":"2026-06-13T21:12:15.124Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_329b78277c5048faaf53a248","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[31;1mC:\\Python\\Lib\\site-packages\\requests\\__init__.py:113: RequestsDependencyWarning: urllib3 (2.1.0) or chardet (7.2.0)/charset_normalizer (3.4.6) doesn't match a supported version![0m\r\n[31;1m  warnings.warn([0m\r\n============================================================\r\nPTZ �ٶȾ�ȷ��֤\r\n============================================================\r\n\r\n�ص�HOMEλ��...\r\n��ǰλ��: azimuth=1800, elevation=450\r\n\r\n��ʼ����...\r\n\r\n�����١�pan=50\r\n  ��ʼλ��: az=1800\r\n  ����λ��: az=975\r\n  �ƶ���: 825��, �ٶ�: 412.5��/��\r\n\r\n�����١�pan=100\r\n  ��ʼλ��: az=1800\r\n  ����λ��: az=3126\r\n  �ƶ���: 1326��, �ٶ�: 663.0��/��\r\n\r\n�����١�pan=200\r\n  ��ʼλ��: az=1800\r\n  ����λ��: az=3126\r\n  �ƶ���: 1326��, �ٶ�: 663.0��/��\r\n\r\n����졿pan=400\r\n  ��ʼλ��: az=1800\r\n  ����λ��: az=3136\r\n  �ƶ���: 1336��, �ٶ�: 668.0��/��\r\n\r\n============================================================\r\n��֤���\r\n============================================================\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"quiet-coral","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[31;1mC:\\Python\\Lib\\site-packages\\requests\\__init__.py:113: RequestsDependencyWarning: urllib3 (2.1.0) or chardet (7.2.0)/charset_normalizer (3.4.6) doesn't match a supported version![0m\r\n[31;1m  warnings.warn([0m\r\n============================================================\r\nPTZ �ٶȾ�ȷ��֤\r\n============================================================\r\n\r\n�ص�HOMEλ��...\r\n��ǰλ��: azimuth=1800, elevation=450\r\n\r\n��ʼ����...\r\n\r\n�����١�pan=50\r\n  ��ʼλ��: az=1800\r\n  ����λ��: az=975\r\n  �ƶ���: 825��, �ٶ�: 412.5��/��\r\n\r\n�����١�pan=100\r\n  ��ʼλ��: az=1800\r\n  ����λ��: az=3126\r\n  �ƶ���: 1326��, �ٶ�: 663.0��/��\r\n\r\n�����١�pan=200\r\n  ��ʼλ��: az=1800\r\n  ����λ��: az=3126\r\n  �ƶ���: 1326��, �ٶ�: 663.0��/��\r\n\r\n����졿pan=400\r\n  ��ʼλ��: az=1800\r\n  ����λ��: az=3136\r\n  �ƶ���: 1336��, �ٶ�: 668.0��/��\r\n\r\n============================================================\r\n��֤���\r\n============================================================\r\n","name":"cd astrohub;"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1781385135124}}
{"type":"message","id":"c25a1136","parentId":"070c0320","timestamp":"2026-06-13T21:12:38.746Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老板，测试结果非常关键！\n\n## 测试结果分析\n\n| ISAPI pan值 | 2秒移动量 | 实际速度 |\n|------------|----------|---------|\n| 50 | 825度 | 412.5度/秒 |\n| 100 | 1326度 | 663度/秒 |\n| 200 | 1326度 | 663度/秒 |\n| 400 | 1336度 | 668度/秒 |\n\n**关键发现**：\n- **pan=100、200、400 的移动量几乎相同！**\n- 说明 **ISAPI continuous_move 的有效速度上限约为 100**\n- 超过 100 的值被限制\n\n**但之前的测试显示 pan=50 移动了 103度，现在却是 825度？**\n\n这可能是因为：\n1. 设备固件版本不同\n2. 移动时间计算有误\n3. 限位影响\n\n让我检查设备返回的速度范围配置："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_491de3609e164d5db3044727","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd astrohub; python -c \"\nimport os\nos.environ.pop('http_proxy', None)\nimport requests\nfrom requests.auth import HTTPDigestAuth\nimport re\n\nip = '192.168.5.72'\nauth = HTTPDigestAuth('admin', 'Nftw1357')\n\n# 获取 capabilities\nr = requests.get(f'http://{ip}/ISAPI/PTZCtrl/channels/1/capabilities', auth=auth, timeout=15, proxies={'http':None,'https':None})\nif r.status_code == 200:\n    # 提取速度范围\n    pan_min = re.search(r'<XRange>.*?<Min>(-?\\d+)</Min>.*?</XRange>', r.text, re.DOTALL)\n    pan_max = re.search(r'<XRange>.*?<Max>(\\d+)</Max>.*?</XRange>', r.text, re.DOTALL)\n    \n    print('=== PTZ Capabilities ===')\n    \n    # ContinuousPanTiltSpace\n    match = re.search(r'<ContinuousPanTiltSpace>.*?<Min>(-?\\d+)</Min>.*?<Max>(\\d+)</Max>.*?</ContinuousPanTiltSpace>', r.text, re.DOTALL)\n    if match:\n        print(f'ContinuousPanTiltSpace: {match.group(1)} to {match.group(2)}')\n    \n    # ContinuousZoomSpace  \n    match = re.search(r'<ContinuousZoomSpace>.*?<Min>(-?\\d+)</Min>.*?<Max>(\\d+)</Max>.*?</ContinuousZoomSpace>', r.text, re.DOTALL)\n    if match:\n        print(f'ContinuousZoomSpace: {match.group(1)} to {match.group(2)}')\n\n# 获取 PTZChannel 配置\nr = requests.get(f'http://{ip}/ISAPI/PTZCtrl/channels/1/', auth=auth, timeout=15, proxies={'http':None,'https':None})\nif r.status_code == 200:\n    print('\\\\n=== PTZChannel ===')\n    pan_max = re.search(r'<panMaxSpeed>(\\d+)</panMaxSpeed>', r.text)\n    tilt_max = re.search(r'<tiltMaxSpeed>(\\d+)</tiltMaxSpeed>', r.text)\n    if pan_max:\n        print(f'panMaxSpeed: {pan_max.group(1)}')\n    if tilt_max:\n        print(f'tiltMaxSpeed: {tilt_max.group(1)}')\n\" 2>&1","timeout":20,"workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":120484,"output":775,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":121259,"cost":{"input":0.120484,"output":0.00248,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.12296399999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781385135127,"responseId":"cht000ee23a@dx19ec2d419ddb893102"}}
