{"type":"message","id":"0891ede4","parentId":"7eb451bc","timestamp":"2026-06-13T21:13:05.078Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老板，设备返回的信息明确了：\n\n## 官方 ISAPI 速度规范\n\n```\nContinuousPanTiltSpace: -100 to 100  （ISAPI continuous_move 速度范围）\nContinuousZoomSpace: -100 to 100     （Zoom 速度范围）\n\npanMaxSpeed: 400   （Pan 最大机械速度 400度/秒）\ntiltMaxSpeed: 200  （Tilt 最大机械速度 200度/秒）\n```\n\n**关键理解**：\n- **ISAPI continuous_move 的速度范围确实是 -100 到 100**\n- **panMaxSpeed=400 是设备的机械速度上限，不是 ISAPI 参数范围**\n\n所以档位映射应该是：\n| 档位 | ISAPI速度 | 实际速度 |\n|------|----------|---------|\n| 1 | 14 | 14% × 400 = 56度/秒 |\n| 2 | 28 | 28% × 400 = 112度/秒 |\n| 3 | 43 | 43% × 400 = 172度/秒 |\n| 4 | 57 | 57% × 400 = 228度/秒（默认）|\n| 5 | 71 | 71% × 400 = 284度/秒 |\n| 6 | 86 | 86% × 400 = 344度/秒 |\n| 7 | 100 | 100% × 400 = 400度/秒（最快）|\n\n我之前的映射（1→57, 7→400）是错的！正确的映射应该是 **1→14, 7→100**。\n\n让我恢复正确的映射："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-51d62626b1514f5a8db0cf398b4d3a64","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"        # Pan/Tilt operations - 官方档位映射\n        # 官方 web 端: 1-7 档，默认 4 档\n        # ISAPI continuous_move 速度范围: -100 到 100\n        # panMaxSpeed=400 是机械速度上限，ISAPI速度=100对应400度/秒\n        # 档位映射: 1→14, 2→28, 3→43, 4→57, 5→71, 6→86, 7→100\n        pan_val, tilt_val = self.DIRECTION_MAP[direction]\n        \n        # 将 1-7 档映射到 ISAPI 速度值 (-100 到 100)\n        if 1 <= speed <= 7:\n            # 官方档位映射 (ISAPI范围 0-100)\n            speed_mapping = {1: 14, 2: 28, 3: 43, 4: 57, 5: 71, 6: 86, 7: 100}\n            isapi_speed = speed_mapping.get(speed, 57)  # 默认档位 4 → 57\n        else:\n            # 兼容：直接使用 0-100 值\n            isapi_speed = min(max(speed, 0), 100)\n        \n        pan = int(pan_val * isapi_speed)\n        tilt = int(tilt_val * isapi_speed)","oldText":"        # Pan/Tilt operations - 官方档位映射\n        # 官方 web 端: 1-7 档，默认 4 档\n        # 官方 ISAPI 速度范围: Pan -400 到 400, Tilt -200 到 200\n        # 档位映射: 1→57, 2→114, 3→171, 4→228, 5→285, 6→342, 7→400\n        # 参考: 测试验证 pan=400 是最大速度, pan=100 被限制到相同速度\n        pan_val, tilt_val = self.DIRECTION_MAP[direction]\n        \n        # 将 1-7 档映射到 ISAPI 速度值\n        if 1 <= speed <= 7:\n            # 官方档位映射 (Pan 最大 400)\n            speed_mapping = {1: 57, 2: 114, 3: 171, 4: 228, 5: 285, 6: 342, 7: 400}\n            isapi_speed = speed_mapping.get(speed, 228)  # 默认档位 4 → 228\n        else:\n            # 兼容旧版：直接使用 0-400 值\n            isapi_speed = min(max(speed, 0), 400)\n        \n        pan = int(pan_val * isapi_speed)\n        tilt = int(tilt_val * isapi_speed * 0.5)  # Tilt 最大 200"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\core\\ptz_manager.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":111298,"output":1076,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":112374,"cost":{"input":0.111298,"output":0.0034432000000000004,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.11474119999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781385159567,"responseId":"cht000df0fc@dx19ec2d47c4eb91a742"}}
