{"type":"message","id":"f9cc8552","parentId":"efde07f5","timestamp":"2026-06-13T21:15:44.723Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_a0fd63e1a89d4186aceaf8a9","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[31;1mC:\\Python\\Lib\\site-packages\\requests\\__init__.py:113: RequestsDependencyWarning: urllib3 (2.1.0) or chardet (7.2.0)/charset_normalizer (3.4.6) doesn't match a supported version![0m\r\n[31;1m  warnings.warn([0m\r\n==================================================\r\nPTZ �ٶ���֤ (���м�λ�ÿ�ʼ)\r\n==================================================\r\n\r\n�ƶ����м�λ�� az=1800...\r\n��ǰλ��: az=1800\r\n\r\n���� 0.5�� �ƶ�:\r\nISAPI= 14: �ƶ�  48��, �ٶ�Լ  96��/��\r\nISAPI= 28: �ƶ�  90��, �ٶ�Լ 180��/��\r\nISAPI= 57: �ƶ� 232��, �ٶ�Լ 464��/��\r\nISAPI= 86: �ƶ� 346��, �ٶ�Լ 692��/��\r\nISAPI=100: �ƶ� 538��, �ٶ�Լ1076��/��\r\n\r\n��֤���!\r\nISAPI=100 ��ӦԼ 400��/�� (�豸����ٶ�)\r\n\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"neat-falcon","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[31;1mC:\\Python\\Lib\\site-packages\\requests\\__init__.py:113: RequestsDependencyWarning: urllib3 (2.1.0) or chardet (7.2.0)/charset_normalizer (3.4.6) doesn't match a supported version![0m\r\n[31;1m  warnings.warn([0m\r\n==================================================\r\nPTZ �ٶ���֤ (���м�λ�ÿ�ʼ)\r\n==================================================\r\n\r\n�ƶ����м�λ�� az=1800...\r\n��ǰλ��: az=1800\r\n\r\n���� 0.5�� �ƶ�:\r\nISAPI= 14: �ƶ�  48��, �ٶ�Լ  96��/��\r\nISAPI= 28: �ƶ�  90��, �ٶ�Լ 180��/��\r\nISAPI= 57: �ƶ� 232��, �ٶ�Լ 464��/��\r\nISAPI= 86: �ƶ� 346��, �ٶ�Լ 692��/��\r\nISAPI=100: �ƶ� 538��, �ٶ�Լ1076��/��\r\n\r\n��֤���!\r\nISAPI=100 ��ӦԼ 400��/�� (�豸����ٶ�)\r\n","name":"cd astrohub;"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1781385344723}}
{"type":"message","id":"020d6d83","parentId":"f9cc8552","timestamp":"2026-06-13T21:16:07.354Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老板，测试结果显示速度比预期快很多！**ISAPI=100 对应约 1076 度/秒**，这比 panMaxSpeed=400 快多了。\n\n这说明 ISAPI 速度值不是直接对应度/秒，而是一个比例值。让我计算正确的档位映射："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5d23e27015814cd98ae2da1d","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd astrohub; python -c \"\n# 测试结果\n# ISAPI= 14: 96度/秒\n# ISAPI= 28: 180度/秒\n# ISAPI= 57: 464度/秒\n# ISAPI= 86: 692度/秒\n# ISAPI=100: 1076度/秒\n\n# 如果官方7档 = 最快 = panMaxSpeed(400度/秒)\n# 那么 ISAPI 值应该是多少？\n\n# 从测试数据反推: ISAPI=100 对应 1076度/秒\n# 要达到 400度/秒，ISAPI 值约为: 400/1076*100 ≈ 37\n\nprint('=== 档位映射计算 ===')\nprint()\n\n# 官方档位 1-7，默认4，最快7\n# 假设档位7 = 400度/秒 (panMaxSpeed)\n# 速度映射应该是线性的\n\n# 计算每个档位对应的速度（度/秒）\nmax_speed = 400  # 度/秒\ngear_speeds = {\n    1: max_speed * 1/7,   # 57\n    2: max_speed * 2/7,   # 114\n    3: max_speed * 3/7,   # 171\n    4: max_speed * 4/7,   # 228 (默认)\n    5: max_speed * 5/7,   # 285\n    6: max_speed * 6/7,   # 342\n    7: max_speed * 7/7,   # 400 (最快)\n}\n\n# 从测试数据计算 ISAPI 到速度的映射\n# ISAPI=100 对应 1076度/秒\n# ISAPI=57 对应 464度/秒\n# ISAPI=28 对应 180度/秒\n# ISAPI=14 对应 96度/秒\n\n# 反向计算 ISAPI 值\nprint('档位映射（档位 → 度/秒 → ISAPI值）:')\nprint()\nfor gear in range(1, 8):\n    speed_deg = gear_speeds[gear]\n    # 从测试数据插值计算 ISAPI 值\n    # 近似公式: ISAPI ≈ speed_deg / 10.76\n    isapi = round(speed_deg / 10.76)\n    print(f'  档位{gear}: {speed_deg:.0f}度/秒 → ISAPI={isapi}')\n\"","timeout":10,"workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":125301,"output":659,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":125960,"cost":{"input":0.125301,"output":0.0021088,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1274098}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781385344725,"responseId":"cht000d7963@dx19ec2d74f73ba60352"}}
{"type":"message","id":"40271b1a","parentId":"020d6d83","timestamp":"2026-06-13T21:16:07.820Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_5d23e27015814cd98ae2da1d","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== ��λӳ����� ===\r\n\r\n��λӳ�䣨��λ �� ��/�� �� ISAPIֵ��:\r\n\r\n  ��λ1: 57��/�� �� ISAPI=5\r\n  ��λ2: 114��/�� �� ISAPI=11\r\n  ��λ3: 171��/�� �� ISAPI=16\r\n  ��λ4: 229��/�� �� ISAPI=21\r\n  ��λ5: 286��/�� �� ISAPI=27\r\n  ��λ6: 343��/�� �� ISAPI=32\r\n  ��λ7: 400��/�� �� ISAPI=37"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":429,"aggregated":"=== ��λӳ����� ===\r\n\r\n��λӳ�䣨��λ �� ��/�� �� ISAPIֵ��:\r\n\r\n  ��λ1: 57��/�� �� ISAPI=5\r\n  ��λ2: 114��/�� �� ISAPI=11\r\n  ��λ3: 171��/�� �� ISAPI=16\r\n  ��λ4: 229��/�� �� ISAPI=21\r\n  ��λ5: 286��/�� �� ISAPI=27\r\n  ��λ6: 343��/�� �� ISAPI=32\r\n  ��λ7: 400��/�� �� ISAPI=37","cwd":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1781385367820}}
{"type":"message","id":"5a4e8c64","parentId":"40271b1a","timestamp":"2026-06-13T21:16:29.638Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老板，测试数据揭示了关键信息！ISAPI 值不是直接对应速度百分比，而是与速度成正比。\n\n根据测试结果，正确的档位映射应该是：\n\n| 档位 | 目标速度(度/秒) | ISAPI值 |\n|------|----------------|---------|\n| 1 | 57 | 5 |\n| 2 | 114 | 11 |\n| 3 | 171 | 16 |\n| 4 | 229 | 21（默认）|\n| 5 | 286 | 27 |\n| 6 | 343 | 32 |\n| 7 | 400 | 37（最快）|\n\n让我更新代码："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-b473074e28fd4ef8af9902b3865b1cf3","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"        # Pan/Tilt operations - 官方档位映射\n        # 官方 web 端: 1-7 档，默认 4 档\n        # 测试验证: ISAPI值与速度成正比，ISAPI=100对应约1076度/秒\n        # panMaxSpeed=400度/秒，档位7对应ISAPI约37\n        # 档位映射: 1→5, 2→11, 3→16, 4→21, 5→27, 6→32, 7→37\n        pan_val, tilt_val = self.DIRECTION_MAP[direction]\n        \n        # 将 1-7 档映射到 ISAPI 速度值\n        if 1 <= speed <= 7:\n            # 官方档位映射 (档位7 = panMaxSpeed 400度/秒)\n            speed_mapping = {1: 5, 2: 11, 3: 16, 4: 21, 5: 27, 6: 32, 7: 37}\n            isapi_speed = speed_mapping.get(speed, 21)  # 默认档位 4 → 21\n        else:\n            # 兼容：直接使用 ISAPI 值 (0-100)\n            isapi_speed = min(max(speed, 0), 100)\n        \n        pan = int(pan_val * isapi_speed)\n        tilt = int(tilt_val * isapi_speed)","oldText":"        # Pan/Tilt operations - 官方档位映射\n        # 官方 web 端: 1-7 档，默认 4 档\n        # ISAPI continuous_move 速度范围: -100 到 100\n        # panMaxSpeed=400 是机械速度上限，ISAPI速度=100对应400度/秒\n        # 档位映射: 1→14, 2→28, 3→43, 4→57, 5→71, 6→86, 7→100\n        pan_val, tilt_val = self.DIRECTION_MAP[direction]\n        \n        # 将 1-7 档映射到 ISAPI 速度值 (-100 到 100)\n        if 1 <= speed <= 7:\n            # 官方档位映射 (ISAPI范围 0-100)\n            speed_mapping = {1: 14, 2: 28, 3: 43, 4: 57, 5: 71, 6: 86, 7: 100}\n            isapi_speed = speed_mapping.get(speed, 57)  # 默认档位 4 → 57\n        else:\n            # 兼容：直接使用 0-100 值\n            isapi_speed = min(max(speed, 0), 100)\n        \n        pan = int(pan_val * isapi_speed)\n        tilt = int(tilt_val * isapi_speed)"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\core\\ptz_manager.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":115849,"output":861,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":116710,"cost":{"input":0.115849,"output":0.0027552,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.11860419999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781385367822,"responseId":"cht000d1836@dx19ec2d7a982b894142"}}
