{"type":"message","id":"70982957","parentId":"e15d84d3","timestamp":"2026-06-13T21:18:45.015Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老板，测试结果明确了！\n\n## ISAPI 值与速度对应关系\n\n| ISAPI值 | 实际速度 |\n|---------|---------|\n| 37 | 188 度/秒 |\n| **50** | **390 度/秒** ≈ 400度/秒 |\n| 70 | 606 度/秒 |\n| 86 | 740 度/秒 |\n| 100 | 1018 度/秒 |\n\n**要达到 panMaxSpeed=400度/秒，ISAPI 值应该是 50！**\n\n现在重新计算档位映射："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1b6578d271644711840623e7","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd astrohub; python -c \"\n# 目标: 档位7 = 400度/秒 = ISAPI 50\n# 档位1 = 400/7 ≈ 57度/秒\n# 线性映射\n\nmax_speed = 400  # 度/秒 (档位7)\nmax_isapi = 50   # ISAPI值 (对应400度/秒)\n\nprint('=== 正确的档位映射 ===')\nprint()\nprint(f'{\\\"档位\\\":<6} {\\\"速度(度/秒)\\\":<12} {\\\"ISAPI值\\\"}')\nprint('-'*30)\n\nfor gear in range(1, 8):\n    target_speed = max_speed * gear / 7\n    isapi = round(max_isapi * gear / 7)\n    print(f'{gear:<6} {target_speed:<12.0f} {isapi}')\n\nprint()\nprint('档位7 (ISAPI=50) = 400度/秒 = panMaxSpeed')\n\"","timeout":5,"workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":129535,"output":382,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":129917,"cost":{"input":0.12953499999999998,"output":0.0012224,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1307574}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781385506812,"responseId":"cht000d941f@dx19ec2d9cddcba60352"}}
