{"type":"message","id":"d9f2c6f6","parentId":"a9ebf868","timestamp":"2026-06-13T21:19:00.526Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_0d133830948d4910bc6c4816","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== ��λӳ�� ===\r\n\r\n��λ  �ٶ�  ISAPI\r\n--------------------\r\n1     57    7\r\n2     114    14\r\n3     171    21\r\n4     229    29\r\n5     286    36\r\n6     343    43\r\n7     400    50\r\n\r\n��λ7 (ISAPI=50) = 400��/��"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":461,"aggregated":"=== ��λӳ�� ===\r\n\r\n��λ  �ٶ�  ISAPI\r\n--------------------\r\n1     57    7\r\n2     114    14\r\n3     171    21\r\n4     229    29\r\n5     286    36\r\n6     343    43\r\n7     400    50\r\n\r\n��λ7 (ISAPI=50) = 400��/��","cwd":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1781385540526}}
{"type":"message","id":"e643b7ab","parentId":"d9f2c6f6","timestamp":"2026-06-13T21:19:08.886Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老板，正确的档位映射是：\n\n| 档位 | 速度(度/秒) | ISAPI值 |\n|------|------------|---------|\n| 1 | 57 | **7** |\n| 2 | 114 | **14** |\n| 3 | 171 | **21** |\n| 4 | 229 | **29**（默认）|\n| 5 | 286 | **36** |\n| 6 | 343 | **43** |\n| 7 | 400 | **50**（最快）|\n\n让我更新代码："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_fd6260f1df7445a398053d9a","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"        # Pan/Tilt operations - 官方档位映射\n        # 官方 web 端: 1-7 档，默认 4 档\n        # 测试验证: ISAPI=50 对应 400度/秒 (panMaxSpeed)\n        # 档位映射: 1→7, 2→14, 3→21, 4→29, 5→36, 6→43, 7→50\n        pan_val, tilt_val = self.DIRECTION_MAP[direction]\n        \n        # 将 1-7 档映射到 ISAPI 速度值\n        if 1 <= speed <= 7:\n            # 官方档位映射 (档位7 = ISAPI 50 = panMaxSpeed 400度/秒)\n            speed_mapping = {1: 7, 2: 14, 3: 21, 4: 29, 5: 36, 6: 43, 7: 50}\n            isapi_speed = speed_mapping.get(speed, 29)  # 默认档位 4 → 29\n        else:\n            # 兼容：直接使用 ISAPI 值 (0-100)\n            isapi_speed = min(max(speed, 0), 100)\n        \n        pan = int(pan_val * isapi_speed)\n        tilt = int(tilt_val * isapi_speed)","oldText":"        # Pan/Tilt operations - 官方档位映射\n        # 官方 web 端: 1-7 档，默认 4 档\n        # 测试验证: ISAPI值与速度成正比，ISAPI=100对应约1076度/秒\n        # panMaxSpeed=400度/秒，档位7对应ISAPI约37\n        # 档位映射: 1→5, 2→11, 3→16, 4→21, 5→27, 6→32, 7→37\n        pan_val, tilt_val = self.DIRECTION_MAP[direction]\n        \n        # 将 1-7 档映射到 ISAPI 速度值\n        if 1 <= speed <= 7:\n            # 官方档位映射 (档位7 = panMaxSpeed 400度/秒)\n            speed_mapping = {1: 5, 2: 11, 3: 16, 4: 21, 5: 27, 6: 32, 7: 37}\n            isapi_speed = speed_mapping.get(speed, 21)  # 默认档位 4 → 21\n        else:\n            # 兼容：直接使用 ISAPI 值 (0-100)\n            isapi_speed = min(max(speed, 0), 100)\n        \n        pan = int(pan_val * isapi_speed)\n        tilt = int(tilt_val * isapi_speed)"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\core\\ptz_manager.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":120246,"output":832,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":121078,"cost":{"input":0.12024599999999999,"output":0.0026624,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.12290839999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781385540528,"responseId":"cht000d305d@dx19ec2da36b1b85e102"}}
