{"type":"message","id":"38fe5a81","parentId":"fd77fb97","timestamp":"2026-06-13T21:21:55.113Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老板，我明白了！\n\n**问题**：\n1. ISAPI 值就是数值，不是度/秒\n2. 前端滑动条还是 1-100，应该改成 1-7 档\n\n**但我不能修改 index.html（您说的控制端网页）**。\n\n后端我已经修复了档位映射：\n- 档位 1-7 映射到 ISAPI 值\n- 档位 7 = ISAPI 50\n\n**前端滑动条 1-100 的问题**：这是 index.html 的问题，需要修改前端代码才能改成 1-7 档下拉菜单。\n\n您确认要我修改 index.html 吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":124385,"output":148,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":124533,"cost":{"input":0.124385,"output":0.0004736,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1248586}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781385705005,"responseId":"cht000d3fc7@dx19ec2dcd192ba5a412"}}
{"type":"message","id":"385c137c","parentId":"38fe5a81","timestamp":"2026-06-13T21:23:08.131Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:8447197723\",\n  \"message_id\": \"35153\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-06-14 05:23 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yixing Zhang (8447197723)\",\n  \"id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"name\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"username\": \"ZhangyixingTG\"\n}\n```\n\n我说是滑动条，1~7，7个档，默认在4档。这么难理解吗？什么下拉菜单？！\n你刚才测试的结果是\n• ISAPI=100 → 1076度/秒\n• ISAPI=57 → 464度/秒\n然后，你的意思是，速度50比速度100还快？"}],"timestamp":1781385788126}}
{"type":"message","id":"0c6a84af","parentId":"385c137c","timestamp":"2026-06-13T21:23:21.013Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老板，我理解了！\n\n**问题1：滑动条范围**\n滑动条改成 1-7，默认值 4。我需要修改 index.html。\n\n**问题2：ISAPI 速度值**\n测试结果显示：\n- ISAPI=100 → 1076 度/秒\n- ISAPI=57 → 464 度/秒\n\n**ISAPI=50 应该比 ISAPI=100 慢**，不是更快！\n\n所以档位映射应该是：\n- 档位 7（最快）= ISAPI 100\n- 档位 4（默认）= ISAPI 57\n- 档位 1（最慢）= ISAPI 14\n\n让我立即修复："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_de81c5bfe1d744088c619c66","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"        # Pan/Tilt operations - 官方档位映射\n        # 官方 web 端: 1-7 档，默认 4 档\n        # ISAPI 速度值: 档位7=ISAPI 100 (最快)\n        # 档位映射: 1→14, 2→28, 3→43, 4→57, 5→71, 6→86, 7→100\n        pan_val, tilt_val = self.DIRECTION_MAP[direction]\n        \n        if 1 <= speed <= 7:\n            speed_mapping = {1: 14, 2: 28, 3: 43, 4: 57, 5: 71, 6: 86, 7: 100}\n            isapi_speed = speed_mapping.get(speed, 57)\n        else:\n            isapi_speed = min(max(speed, 0), 100)\n        \n        pan = int(pan_val * isapi_speed)\n        tilt = int(tilt_val * isapi_speed)","oldText":"        # Pan/Tilt operations - 官方档位映射\n        # 官方 web 端: 1-7 档，默认 4 档\n        # 测试验证: ISAPI=50 对应 400度/秒 (panMaxSpeed)\n        # 档位映射: 1→7, 2→14, 3→21, 4→29, 5→36, 6→43, 7→50\n        pan_val, tilt_val = self.DIRECTION_MAP[direction]\n        \n        # 将 1-7 档映射到 ISAPI 速度值\n        if 1 <= speed <= 7:\n            # 官方档位映射 (档位7 = ISAPI 50 = panMaxSpeed 400度/秒)\n            speed_mapping = {1: 7, 2: 14, 3: 21, 4: 29, 5: 36, 6: 43, 7: 50}\n            isapi_speed = speed_mapping.get(speed, 29)  # 默认档位 4 → 29\n        else:\n            # 兼容：直接使用 ISAPI 值 (0-100)\n            isapi_speed = min(max(speed, 0), 100)\n        \n        pan = int(pan_val * isapi_speed)\n        tilt = int(tilt_val * isapi_speed)"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\core\\ptz_manager.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":124759,"output":767,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":125526,"cost":{"input":0.124759,"output":0.0024544000000000002,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1272134}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781385788131,"responseId":"cht000dc284@dx19ec2de1430b87f702"}}
