�̨\"\r\n   Ԫ��: tag=DIV, id=None, class=ptz-panel, text=\"\"\r\n   Ԫ��: tag=DIV, id=None, class=ptz-panel-content position-relative, text=\"\"\r\n   Ԫ��: tag=IMG, id=None, class=position-absolute ptz-panel-content-bg, text=\"\"\r\n   Ԫ��: tag=I, id=None, class=ptz-icon-ptz-left-up position-absolute, text=\"\"\r\n   Ԫ��: tag=I, id=None, class=ptz-icon-ptz-up position-absolute, text=\"\"\r\n   Ԫ��: tag=I, id=None, class=ptz-icon-ptz-right-up position-absolute, text=\"\"\r\n   Ԫ��: tag=I, id=None, class=ptz-icon-ptz-left position-absolute, text=\"\"\r\n   Ԫ��: tag=DIV, id=None, class=ptz-control-auto, text=\"\"\r\n   Ԫ��: tag=I, id=None, class=ic-ptz_rotate position-absolute, text=\"\"\r\n   Ԫ��: tag=I, id=None, class=ic-ptz_rotate position-absolute, text=\"\"\r\n   Ԫ��: tag=I, id=None, class=ptz-icon-ptz-right position-absolute, text=\"\"\r\n   Ԫ��: tag=I, id=None, class=ptz-icon-ptz-left-down position-absolute, text=\"\"\r\n   Ԫ��: tag=I, id=None, class=ptz-icon-ptz-down position-absolute, text=\"\"\r\n   Ԫ��: tag=I, id=None, class=ptz-icon-ptz-right-down position-absolute, text=\"\"\r\n   Ԫ��: tag=DIV, id=None, class=ptz-slider, text=\"��\r\n��\"\r\n   Ԫ��: tag=DIV, id=None, class=ptz-slider-text, text=\"��\r\n��\"\r\n   Ԫ��: tag=DIV, id=None, class=ptz-other, text=\"\"\r\n\r\n=== ������ ===\r\n��ͼ����:\r\n  - official_1_login.png\r\n  - official_2_filled.png\r\n  - official_3_after_login.png\r\n  - official_4_preview.png\r\n\r\n��������ִ� 60 �빩�ֶ����...\n\nProcess exited with signal SIGKILL."}],"details":{"status":"failed","sessionId":"marine-sage","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"=== ���ٷ� Web �� PTZ �ٶ����� ===\r\n\r\n1. ���ʹٷ� Web ��...\r\n   ��ͼ: official_1_login.png\r\n2. �ȴ���¼����...\r\n   �ҵ� 3 �� input Ԫ��\r\n   �ɼ�: type=text, id=None, name=None\r\n   �ɼ�: type=password, id=None, name=None\r\n3. ��д��¼��Ϣ...\r\n   �û���: admin\r\n   ����: Nftw1357\r\n   ��ͼ: official_2_filled.png\r\n4. �����¼��ť...\r\n   �ҵ� 1 ����ť\r\n   ��ť: text=\"��¼\", type=button, class=e