{"type":"message","id":"29f9e4de","parentId":"2ecefcf7","timestamp":"2026-06-13T22:05:21.396Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老板，检查完成！\n\n## 检查结果\n\n找到了 PTZ 控制区域：\n- `class=ptz-root` - PTZ 根容器\n- `class=ptz-slider` - **PTZ 滑动条**\n- `class=ptz-slider-text` - 滑动条文本（显示\"慢\"和\"快\"）\n\n**关键发现**：\n- 官方 Web 端使用的是 **滑动条**，不是下拉菜单\n- 滑动条两端显示\"慢\"和\"快\"\n\n但没有找到具体的 `min`/`max` 值。让我检查截图："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f61ed546818d4c31913ae2cc","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\official_5_preview.png"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":67777,"output":168,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67945,"cost":{"input":0.06777699999999999,"output":0.0005376000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.06831459999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781388314117,"responseId":"cht000d413e@dx19ec3048dd0b894142"}}
