{"type":"message","id":"ad1b93f9","parentId":"80cc6f37","timestamp":"2026-06-13T22:15:08.095Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老板，`continuous_move` 方法是正确的，它直接发送传入的 pan 值。\n\n让我检查 `ptz_move` 方法中档位映射后实际发送的值："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-ecc96b0338d1485080ab63e6fd104a7e","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":100,"offset":2355,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\core\\ptz_manager.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":73601,"output":84,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73685,"cost":{"input":0.073601,"output":0.00026880000000000003,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0738698}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781388900700,"responseId":"cht000db418@dx19ec30d821ab91a742"}}
{"type":"message","id":"2ebc8003","parentId":"ad1b93f9","timestamp":"2026-06-13T22:15:08.103Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-ecc96b0338d1485080ab63e6fd104a7e","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\r\n        if direction not in self.DIRECTION_MAP:\r\n            LOG.log(\"warning\", f\"PTZ 移动: 未知方向 {direction}\")\r\n            return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"未知方向: {direction}\"}\r\n\r\n        # Pan/Tilt operations - 官方档位映射\r\n        # 官方 web 端: 1-7 档，默认 4 档\r\n        # ISAPI 速度值: 档位7=ISAPI 100 (最快)\r\n        # 档位映射: 1→14, 2→28, 3→43, 4→57, 5→71, 6→86, 7→100\r\n        pan_val, tilt_val = self.DIRECTION_MAP[direction]\r\n        \r\n        if 1 <= speed <= 7:\r\n            speed_mapping = {1: 14, 2: 28, 3: 43, 4: 57, 5: 71, 6: 86, 7: 100}\r\n            isapi_speed = speed_mapping.get(speed, 57)\r\n        else:\r\n            isapi_speed = min(max(speed, 0), 100)\r\n        \r\n        pan = int(pan_val * isapi_speed)\r\n        tilt = int(tilt_val * isapi_speed)\r\n\r\n        success = ctrl.continuous_move(pan=pan, tilt=tilt)\r\n        if success:\r\n            LOG.log(\"done\", f\"PTZ 移动成功: device={ip} direction={direction} speed={speed}(档位)→isapi={isapi_speed}\")\r\n        else:\r\n            LOG.log(\"failed\", f\"PTZ 移动失败: device={ip} direction={direction}\")\r\n        return {\r\n            \"success\": success,\r\n            \"message\": f\"PTZ 移动: {direction} (档位={speed})\",\r\n            \"direction\": direction,\r\n            \"speed\": speed,\r\n            \"isapi_speed\": isapi_speed,\r\n        }\r\n\r\n    def ptz_home(self, ip: str) -> dict:\r\n        ctrl, err = self._get_controller(ip)\r\n        if err:\r\n            return {\"success\": False, \"message\": err}\r\n\r\n        success = ctrl.goto_preset(10)  # 直接调用 goto_preset(10)\r\n        return {\r\n            \"success\": success,\r\n            \"message\": \"归位成功\" if success else \"归位失败\",\r\n        }\r\n\r\n    def ptz_stop(self, ip: str) -> dict:\r\n        ctrl, err = self._get_controller(ip)\r\n        if err:\r\n            return {\"success\": False, \"message\": err}\r\n\r\n        success = ctrl.stop_move()\r\n        return {\r\n            \"success\": success,\r\n            \"message\": \"停止成功\" if success else \"停止失败\",\r\n        }\r\n\r\n    def ptz_preset(self, ip: str, preset_id: int) -> dict:\r\n        ctrl, err = self._get_controller(ip)\r\n        if err:\r\n            return {\"success\": False, \"message\": err}\r\n\r\n        success = ctrl.goto_preset(preset_id)\r\n        return {\r\n            \"success\": success,\r\n            \"message\": f\"预置位 {preset_id} {'成功' if success else '失败'}\",\r\n            \"preset_id\": preset_id,\r\n        }\r\n\r\n    def set_preset(self, ip: str, preset_id: int) -> dict:\r\n        \"\"\"设置当前位置为预置点。\r\n\r\n        路由: POST /api/v1/ptz/{device_id}/preset/{preset_id}/set\r\n        \"\"\"\r\n        ctrl, err = self._get_controller(ip)\r\n        if err:\r\n            return {\"success\": False, \"message\": err}\r\n\r\n        success = ctrl.set_preset(preset_id)\r\n        return {\r\n            \"success\": success,\r\n            \"message\": f\"预置位 {preset_id} 设置{'成功' if success else '失败'}\",\r\n            \"preset_id\": preset_id,\r\n        }\r\n\r\n    def ptz_list_presets(self, ip: str) -> dict:\r\n        \"\"\"获取设备预置点列表。\r\n\r\n        路由: GET /api/v1/ptz/{device_id}/presets\r\n        \"\"\"\r\n        ctrl, err = self._get_controller(ip)\r\n        if err:\r\n            return {\"success\": False, \"message\": err}\r\n\r\n        presets = ctrl.list_presets()\r\n        return {\r\n            \"success\": True,\r\n            \"presets\": presets,\r\n            \"count\": len(presets),\r\n        }\r\n\r\n    def ptz_absolute(self, ip: str, pan: float, tilt: float,\r\n\n[453 more lines in file. Use offset=2455 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781388908103}}
{"type":"message","id":"ebf7c986","parentId":"2ebc8003","timestamp":"2026-06-13T22:15:24.873Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老板，我找到问题了！\n\n**第 2375 行**：\n```python\npan = int(pan_val * isapi_speed)\n```\n\n这里 `pan_val` 是方向值（1 或 -1），乘以 `isapi_speed` 后得到最终值。\n\n**档位7时**：\n- `isapi_speed = 100`\n- `pan_val = 1`（向右）\n- `pan = 1 * 100 = 100`\n\n**理论上应该发送 pan=100，速度应该是 1058 度/秒，但实际只有 66 度/秒！**\n\n让我检查日志输出，看实际发送的是什么："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_57112c7a5f1548c4a424ca32","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd astrohub; python -c \"\nimport os\nos.environ.pop('http_proxy', None)\nimport requests\nfrom requests.auth import HTTPDigestAuth\nimport time\nimport re\n\nip = '192.168.5.72'\nauth = HTTPDigestAuth('admin', 'Nftw1357')\nbase = f'http://{ip}/ISAPI/PTZCtrl/channels/1'\n\ndef get_pos():\n    r = requests.get(f'{base}/status', auth=auth, timeout=10, proxies={'http':None,'https':None})\n    if r.status_code == 200:\n        az = re.search(r'<azimuth>(\\d+)</azimuth>', r.text)\n        return int(az.group(1)) if az else 0\n    return 0\n\ndef abs_move(az):\n    xml = f'<PTZData><AbsoluteHigh><azimuth>{az}</azimuth><elevation>450</elevation><absoluteZoom>10</absoluteZoom></AbsoluteHigh></PTZData>'.encode('utf-8')\n    requests.put(f'{base}/absolute/', data=xml, auth=auth, timeout=10, proxies={'http':None,'https':None})\n    time.sleep(2)\n\nprint('测试 AstroHub API 档位7...')\n\n# 直接调用 API\nurl = 'http://localhost:10280/api/v1/ptz/192.168.5.72/move'\n\n# 移动到中间位置\nabs_move(1800)\ntime.sleep(1)\n\nstart = get_pos()\nprint(f'开始: {start}')\n\n# 发送档位7\nr = requests.post(url, json={'direction': 'right', 'speed': 7}, timeout=10, proxies={'http':None,'https':None})\nprint(f'API响应: {r.status_code}')\nprint(f'响应内容: {r.text}')\n\ntime.sleep(0.5)\n\n# 停止\nr = requests.post(url, json={'direction': 'stop', 'speed': 7}, timeout=10, proxies={'http':None,'https':None})\ntime.sleep(0.3)\n\nend = get_pos()\nprint(f'结束: {end}')\n\ndelta = abs(end - start)\nsp