{"type":"message","id":"a0df5b63","parentId":"0630e6de","timestamp":"2026-06-13T22:17:16.294Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老板，我发现问题了！\n\n**第 1161 行**：\n```python\nxml = f'<PTZData>...'.encode('utf-8')\nresult = self.client.put(f\"{self._ptz_base()}/continuous\", xml)\n```\n\n但 `client.put` 方法定义是：\n```python\ndef put(self, endpoint: str, xml_body: str) -> ISAPIResponse:\n```\n\n**`put` 方法期望 `xml_body` 是字符串，但 `continuous_move` 传的是 bytes！**\n\n`client.put` 内部会再次调用 `.encode('utf-8')`，导致双重编码！\n\n修复："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_bec176041d6c4bf6b74415dc","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"        # 官方格式：<PTZData><pan>{pan}</pan><tilt>{tilt}</tilt><zoom>{zoom}</zoom></PTZData>\n        xml = f'<PTZData><pan>{pan_speed}</pan><tilt>{tilt_speed}</tilt><zoom>{zoom_speed}</zoom></PTZData>'\n        result = self.client.put(f\"{self._ptz_base()}/continuous\", xml)\n        return result.status_code == 200","oldText":"        # 官方格式：<PTZData><pan>{pan}</pan><tilt>{tilt}</tilt><zoom>{zoom}</zoom></PTZData>\n        xml = f'<PTZData><pan>{pan_speed}</pan><tilt>{tilt_speed}</tilt><zoom>{zoom_speed}</zoom></PTZData>'.encode('utf-8')\n        result = self.client.put(f\"{self._ptz_base()}/continuous\", xml)\n        return result.status_code == 200"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\core\\ptz_manager.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":80619,"output":403,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81022,"cost":{"input":0.080619,"output":0.0012896000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0819086}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781389028460,"responseId":"cht000dc6c7@dx19ec30f73dfb85e102"}}
