{"type":"message","id":"286bb3e0","parentId":"0c61295b","timestamp":"2026-06-13T22:33:53.915Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-a0d2edbfb66f47cbbe96f37c8d551a72","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== Playwright ���� AstroHub PTZ ��λ ===\r\n\r\n1. ���� AstroHub...\r\n   ��ͼ: astrohub_home.png\r\n2. ��������̨...\r\n   �������̨�˵�\r\n   ��ͼ: astrohub_console.png\r\n3. չ�� PTZ ��������...\r\n   �۵�״̬: True\r\n   ���չ��\r\n   ��ͼ: astrohub_ptz_expanded.png\r\n4. ���� PTZ �ٶȻ�����...\r\n   ����������: min=1, max=7, value=4\r\n   ��ʾֵ: 4\r\n\r\n5. ���Ը���λ...\r\n   ��λ1: ������ֵ=1, ��ʾֵ=1\r\n   ��λ4: ������ֵ=4, ��ʾֵ=4\r\n   ��λ7: ������ֵ=7, ��ʾֵ=7\r\n\r\n=== ������� ===\r\n��������ִ� 30 ��...\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"faint-atlas","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"=== Playwright ���� AstroHub PTZ ��λ ===\r\n\r\n1. ���� AstroHub...\r\n   ��ͼ: astrohub_home.png\r\n2. ��������̨...\r\n   �������̨�˵�\r\n   ��ͼ: astrohub_console.png\r\n3. չ�� PTZ ��������...\r\n   �۵�״̬: True\r\n   ���չ��\r\n   ��ͼ: astrohub_ptz_expanded.png\r\n4. ���� PTZ �ٶȻ�����...\r\n   ����������: min=1, max=7, value=4\r\n   ��ʾֵ: 4\r\n\r\n5. ���Ը���λ...\r\n   ��λ1: ������ֵ=1, ��ʾֵ=1\r\n   ��λ4: ������ֵ=4, ��ʾֵ=4\r\n   ��λ7: ������ֵ=7, ��ʾֵ=7\r\n\r\n=== ������� ===\r\n��������ִ� 30 ��...\r\n","name":"cd astrohub;"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1781390033915}}
{"type":"message","id":"fa74d943","parentId":"286bb3e0","timestamp":"2026-06-13T22:34:23.380Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老板，Playwright 测试结果：\n\n## AstroHub PTZ 档位测试\n\n**滑动条属性**：`min=1, max=7, value=4` ✅\n\n**档位测试**：\n- 档位1：滑动条值=1, 显示值=1 ✅\n- 档位4：滑动条值=4, 显示值=4 ✅\n- 档位7：滑动条值=7, 显示值=7 ✅\n\n**前端滑动条工作正常！**\n\n现在测试实际 PTZ 移动速度："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-2deb5d74ca68493cb7eb1e2c31f990cf","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"\"\"\"Playwright 测试 AstroHub PTZ 实际移动速度\"\"\"\nimport asyncio\nimport os\nos.environ.pop('http_proxy', None)\nimport requests\nfrom requests.auth import HTTPDigestAuth\nimport time\nimport re\nfrom playwright.async_api import async_playwright\n\nip = '192.168.5.72'\nauth = HTTPDigestAuth('admin', 'Nftw1357')\nbase = f'http://{ip}/ISAPI/PTZCtrl/channels/1'\n\ndef get_position():\n    r = requests.get(f'{base}/status', auth=auth, timeout=10, proxies={'http':None,'https':None})\n    if r.status_code == 200:\n        az = re.search(r'<azimuth>(\\d+)</azimuth>', r.text)\n        return int(az.group(1)) if az else 0\n    return 0\n\ndef absolute_move(azimuth):\n    xml = f'<PTZData><AbsoluteHigh><azimuth>{azimuth}</azimuth><elevation>450</elevation><absoluteZoom>10</absoluteZoom></AbsoluteHigh></PTZData>'.encode('utf-8')\n    requests.put(f'{base}/absolute/', data=xml, auth=auth, timeout=10, proxies={'http':None,'https':None})\n    time.sleep(2)\n\nasync def test_astrohub_ptz_speed():\n    async with async_playwright() as p:\n        browser = await p.chromium.launch(headless=False, slow_mo=300)\n        context = await browser.new_context()\n        page = await context.new_page()\n        \n        print('=== Playwright 测试 AstroHub PTZ 实际移动速度 ===')\n        print()\n        \n        # 访问 AstroHub\n        print('1. 访问 AstroHub...')\n        await page.goto('http://localhost:10280/', wait_until='networkidle')\n        await asyncio.sleep(2)\n        \n        # 进入主控台\n        print('2. 进入主控台...')\n        console_btn = await page.query_selector('[data-page=\"console\"]')\n        if console_btn:\n            await console_btn.click()\n            await asyncio.sleep(1)\n        \n        # 展开 PTZ 控制区域\n        print('3. 展开 PTZ 控制区域...')\n        ptz_section = await page.query_selector('#ptzControlSection')\n        if ptz_section:\n            is_collapsed = await ptz_section.evaluate('el => el.classList.contains(\"collapsed\")')\n            if is_collapsed:\n                header = await ptz_section.query_selector('.collapsible-header')\n                if header:\n                    await header.click()\n                    await asyncio.sleep(0.5)\n        \n        # 测试各档位实际移动速度\n        print('4. 测试各档位实际移动速度...')\n        print()\n        \n        results = {}\n        \n        for gear in [1, 4, 7]:\n            print(f'测试档位 {gear}...')\n            \n            # 设置滑动条值\n            slider = await page.query_selector('#ptzSpeed')\n            if slider:\n                await slider.evaluate(f'el => el.value = \"{gear}\"')\n                await slider.evaluate('el => el.dispatchEvent(new Event(\"input\"))')\n                await slider.evaluate('el => el.dispatchEvent(new Event(\"change\"))')\n            \n            # 移动到中间位置\n            absolute_move(1800)\n            await asyncio.sleep(0.5)\n            \n            # 获取开始位置\n            start_pos = get_position()\n            \n            # 点击向右按钮\n            right_btn = await page.query_selector('.ptz-btn:has-text(\"→\")')\n            if right_btn:\n                await right_btn.click()\n                print(f'   点击向右按钮')\n            \n            # 移动 0.5 秒\n            await asyncio.sleep(0.5)\n            \n            # 停止 (鼠标释放会自动停止)\n            await asyncio.sleep(0.3)\n            \n            # 获取结束位置\n            end_pos = get_position()\n            \n            # 计算速度\n            delta = abs(end_pos - start_pos)\n            speed = delta * 2\n            \n            results[gear] = speed\n            print(f'   开始: {start_pos}, 结束: {end_pos}')\n            print(f'   移动: {delta} 度, 速度: {speed} 度/秒')\n            print()\n        \n        # 对比结果\n        print('=== 对比结果 ===')\n        for gear, speed in results.items():\n            print(f'  档位 {gear}: {speed} 度/秒')\n        \n        # 检查是否有差异\n        if abs(results[1] - results[7]) < 50:\n            print()\n            print('问题: 档位1和档位7速度相近，没有明显差异！')\n        else:\n            print()\n            print(f'档位差异: {results[7] - results[1]} 度/秒')\n        \n        print()\n        print('浏览器保持打开 20 秒...')\n        await asyncio.sleep(20)\n        \n        await browser.close()\n\nif __name__ == '__main__':\n    asyncio.run(test_astrohub_ptz_speed())","path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\tests\\test_astrohub_speed_playwright.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":94806,"output":1247,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":96053,"cost":{"input":0.094806,"output":0.003990400000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0987964}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781390033917,"responseId":"cht000dd8d4@dx19ec31ed123ba5d322"}}
