{"type":"message","id":"d790e7f8","parentId":"dec937af","timestamp":"2026-06-13T22:39:34.389Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老板，API 请求正确！\n\n**测试结果**：\n- 档位 1：`{\"direction\":\"right\",\"speed\":1}` ✅\n- 档位 7：`{\"direction\":\"right\",\"speed\":7}` ✅\n\n**前端发送的 speed 值是正确的！**\n\n问题在**后端处理**！让我检查后端日志，看 `ptz_move` 方法实际接收到的 speed 值："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ab79241e53ea425a8b292e4b","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd astrohub; python -c \"\nimport os\nimport sys\nsys.path.insert(0, '.')\nos.environ.pop('http_proxy', None)\n\nfrom src.core.ptz_manager import PTZManager\n\nmgr = PTZManager()\n\n# 测试档位 1\nprint('测试档位 1:')\nresult = mgr.ptz_move('192.168.5.72', direction='right', speed=1)\nprint(f'  结果: {result}')\n\n# 测试档位 7\nprint()\nprint('测试档位 7:')\nresult = mgr.ptz_move('192.168.5.72', direction='right', speed=7)\nprint(f'  结果: {result}')\n\" 2>&1 | Select-String \"档位|isapi|speed\"","timeout":30,"workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":106477,"output":294,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":106771,"cost":{"input":0.10647699999999999,"output":0.0009408000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1074178}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781390362383,"responseId":"cht000db42f@dx19ec323d3d2ba5b442"}}
