{"type":"message","id":"383e3762","parentId":"eff02662","timestamp":"2026-06-13T22:40:14.552Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_9723a901de624c569e7850f2","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[31;1mC:\\Python\\Lib\\site-packages\\requests\\__init__.py:113: RequestsDependencyWarning: urllib3 (2.1.0) or chardet (7.2.0)/charset_normalizer (3.4.6) doesn't match a supported version![0m\r\n[31;1m  warnings.warn([0m\r\n=== ֱ�Ӳ��� ISAPI ��ͬ PAN ֵ���ٶ� ===\r\n\r\nPAN=14: �ƶ� 47 ��, �ٶ� 94 ��/��\r\nPAN=57: �ƶ� 241 ��, �ٶ� 482 ��/��\r\nPAN=100: �ƶ� 517 ��, �ٶ� 1034 ��/��\r\n\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"tidal-nudibranch","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[31;1mC:\\Python\\Lib\\site-packages\\requests\\__init__.py:113: RequestsDependencyWarning: urllib3 (2.1.0) or chardet (7.2.0)/charset_normalizer (3.4.6) doesn't match a supported version![0m\r\n[31;1m  warnings.warn([0m\r\n=== ֱ�Ӳ��� ISAPI ��ͬ PAN ֵ���ٶ� ===\r\n\r\nPAN=14: �ƶ� 47 ��, �ٶ� 94 ��/��\r\nPAN=57: �ƶ� 241 ��, �ٶ� 482 ��/��\r\nPAN=100: �ƶ� 517 ��, �ٶ� 1034 ��/��\r\n","name":"cd astrohub;"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1781390414552}}
{"type":"message","id":"9a1834cf","parentId":"383e3762","timestamp":"2026-06-13T22:40:50.749Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老板，直接测试 ISAPI 结果正确！\n\n**测试结果**：\n- PAN=14（档位1）：**94 度/秒** ✅\n- PAN=57（档位4）：**482 度/秒** ✅\n- PAN=100（档位7）：**1034 度/秒** ✅\n\n**不同 PAN 值对应不同速度，后端处理完全正确！**\n\n**问题在于 Playwright 测试时所有档位速度相同。**\n\n让我分析 Playwright 测试问题：Playwright 测试显示档位1和档位7都是约 1250 度/秒，这说明 Playwright 测试时**设备已经在快速移动中**，而不是从静止开始。\n\n让我重新运行 Playwright 测试，确保每次测试前设备完全停止："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_709a089996b8452992b613a3","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"\"\"\"Playwright 测试 AstroHub PTZ 实际移动速度 - 修复版\"\"\"\nimport asyncio\nimport os\nos.environ.pop('http_proxy', None)\nimport requests\nfrom requests.auth import HTTPDigestAuth\nimport time\nimport re\nfrom playwright.async_api import async_playwright\n\nip = '192.168.5.72'\nauth = HTTPDigestAuth('admin', 'Nftw1357')\nbase = f'http://{ip}/ISAPI/PTZCtrl/channels/1'\n\ndef get_position():\n    r = requests.get(f'{base}/status', auth=auth, timeout=10, proxies={'http':None,'https':None})\n    if r.status_code == 200:\n        az = re.search(r'<azimuth>(\\d+)</azimuth>', r.text)\n        return int(az.group(1)) if az else 0\n    return 0\n\ndef absolute_move(azimuth):\n    xml = f'<PTZData><AbsoluteHigh><azimuth>{azimuth}</azimuth><elevation>450</elevation><absoluteZoom>10</absoluteZoom></AbsoluteHigh></PTZData>'.encode('utf-8')\n    requests.put(f'{base}/absolute/', data=xml, auth=auth, timeout=10, proxies={'http':None,'https':None})\n    time.sleep(3)\n\ndef stop_move():\n    xml = b'<PTZData><pan>0</pan><tilt>0</tilt><zoom>0</zoom></PTZData>'\n    requests.put(f'{base}/continuous/', data=xml, auth=auth, timeout=10, proxies={'http':None,'https':None})\n\nasync def test_astrohub_ptz_speed():\n    async with async_playwright() as p:\n        browser = await p.chromium.launch(headless=False, slow_mo=200)\n        context = await browser.new_context()\n        page = await context.new_page()\n        \n        print('=== Playwright 测试 AstroHub PTZ 实际移动速度 ===')\n        print()\n        \n        # 访问 AstroHub\n        print('1. 访问 AstroHub...')\n        await page.goto('http://localhost:10280/', wait_until='networkidle')\n        await asyncio.sleep(2)\n        \n        # 进入主控台\n        print('2. 进入主控台...')\n        console_btn = await page.query_selector('[data-page=\"console\"]')\n        if console_btn:\n            await console_btn.click()\n            await asyncio.sleep(1)\n        \n        # 展开 PTZ 控制区域\n        print('3. 展开 PTZ 控制区域...')\n        ptz_section = await page.query_selector('#ptzControlSection')\n        if ptz_section:\n            is_collapsed = await ptz_section.evaluate('el => el.classList.contains(\"collapsed\")')\n            if is_collapsed:\n                header = await ptz_section.query_selector('.collapsible-header')\n                if header:\n                    await header.click()\n                    await asyncio.sleep(1)\n        \n        # 测试各档位实际移动速度\n        print('4. 测试各档位实际移动速度...')\n        print()\n        \n        results = {}\n        \n        for gear in [1, 4, 7]:\n            print(f'测试档位 {gear}...')\n            \n            # 设置滑动条值\n            slider = await page.query_selector('#ptzSpeed')\n            if slider:\n                await slider.evaluate(f'el => el.value = \"{gear}\"')\n                await slider.evaluate('el => el.dispatchEvent(new Event(\"input\"))')\n                await asyncio.sleep(0.3)\n            \n            # 确保设备停止\n            stop_move()\n            \n            # 移动到中间位置并等待完全停止\n            absolute_move(1800)\n            await asyncio.sleep(1)\n            \n            # 获取开始位置\n            start_pos = get_position()\n            print(f'   开始位置: {start_pos}')\n            \n            # 找到向右按钮\n            right_btns = await page.query_selector_all('.ptz-btn')\n            right_btn = None\n            for btn in right_btns:\n                text = await btn.inner_text()\n                if '→' in text:\n                    right_btn = btn\n                    break\n            \n            if right_btn:\n                # 模拟 mousedown\n                await right_btn.dispatch_event('mousedown')\n            \n            # 等待 0.5 秒\n            await asyncio.sleep(0.5)\n            \n            # 释放 (mouseup)\n            if right_btn:\n                await right_btn.dispatch_event('mouseup')\n            \n            # 等待设备停止\n            await asyncio.sleep(0.5)\n            \n            # 确保停止\n            stop_move()\n            await asyncio.sleep(0.3)\n            \n            # 获取结束位置\n            end_pos = get_position()\n            print(f'   结束位置: {end_pos}')\n            \n            # 计算速度\n            delta = abs(end_pos - start_pos)\n            speed = delta * 2\n            \n            results[gear] = speed\n            print(f'   移动: {delta} 度, 速度: {speed} 度/秒')\n            print()\n        \n        # 对比结果\n        print('=== 对比结果 ===')\n        for gear, speed in results.items():\n            print(f'  档位 {gear}: {speed} 度/秒')\n        \n        # 检查是否有差异\n        if results[7] > results[1] * 2:\n            print()\n            print('修复成功！档位差异明显！')\n        elif abs(results[1] - results[7]) < 100:\n            print()\n            print('问题: 档位1和档位7速度相近，没有明显差异！')\n        else:\n            print()\n            print(f'档位差异: {results[7] - results[1]} 度/秒')\n        \n        print()\n        print('浏览器保持打开 15 秒...')\n        await asyncio.sleep(15)\n        \n        await browser.close()\n\nif __name__ == '__main__':\n    asyncio.run(test_astrohub_ptz_speed())","path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\tests\\test_astrohub_speed_fixed.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":108177,"output":1488,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":109665,"cost":{"input":0.108177,"output":0.0047616,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0