nk` 指向**：\n- 路径：`C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub`\n- 启动命令：`python -m uvicorn src.api.main:app --host 0.0.0.0 --port 10280`\n- 访问地址：**http://localhost:10280/**\n\n**双击 `AstroHub.lnk` 即可启动 AstroHub 服务。**\n\n## Tool Failures\n- edit: Validation failed for tool \"edit\": - path: must have required properties path Received arguments: { \"edits\": [ { \"newText\": \" # 登录官方 Web 端\\n print('1. 访问官方 Web 端...')\\n await page.goto('http://192.168.5.72/', wait_until='networkidle')\\n ...\n\n<read-files>\nC:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\official_5_preview.png\nC:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html\n\n</read-files>\n\n<modified-files>\nC:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\HEARTBEAT.md\nC:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\create_shortcut.ps1\nC:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\create_shortcut.vbs\nC:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\core\\ptz_manager.py\nC:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html\nC:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\start_astrohub.bat\nC:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\tests\\compare_ptz_speed.py\nC:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\tests\\inspect_official_ptz.py\nC:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\tests\\test_api_request.py\nC:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\tests\\test_astrohub_playwright.py\n...and 9 more\n\n</modified-files>","firstKeptEntryId":"20ad64c0","tokensBefore":154133,"details":{"readFiles":["C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\official_5_preview.png","C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"],"modifiedFiles":["C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\HEARTBEAT.md","C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astro