{"type":"message","id":"b9a591a0","parentId":"8d88a342","timestamp":"2026-06-13T23:08:55.245Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老板，测试结果已经确认全部通过！\n\n现在更新 HEARTBEAT 和记忆："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-d4088f68889146b2ab6c4d5893070785","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 心跳与任务状态\n\n**最后更新**: 2026-06-14 07:07\n**状态**: v6.52 画面控制修复完成\n**工作空间**: C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\n\n### v6.52 修复内容\n\n| # | 问题 | 修复 | 文件 |\n|---|------|------|------|\n| 1 | 白平衡 R/B 设置失败 | ISAPI 要求小写 `manual`/`auto` | `src/api/router.py` |\n| 2 | 降噪 XML 格式错误 | 添加完整 `<mode>general</mode><GeneralMode>` 结构 | `src/api/router.py` |\n| 3 | 版本号更新 | v6.45 → v6.52 | `src/web/index.html` |\n\n### 测试验证\n\n**白平衡 R/B 设置**: 5/5 通过 ✅\n- 连续5次设置不同值，每次等待1秒\n- PUT=200，GET验证值正确\n\n**降噪设置**: 5/5 通过 ✅\n- 连续5次设置不同值，每次等待1秒\n- PUT=200，GET验证值正确\n\n### 备份位置\n- `backup_20260614_065730/`\n\n### 下一步\n- 修复完成，可以进行前端测试","path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\HEARTBEAT.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":49058,"output":341,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49399,"cost":{"input":0.049058,"output":0.0010912,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0501492}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781392120185,"responseId":"cht000deb7d@dx19ec33ea4ebb8ab282"}}
