{"type":"message","id":"f3146114","parentId":"d91594c6","timestamp":"2026-06-13T23:09:02.635Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"记录修复教训："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c7c48fd7964448a28fef61d6","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 开发教训 - 2026-06-14\n\n## LRN-20260614-001: ISAPI XML 格式大小写敏感\n\n**问题**: 白平衡 R/B 设置 PUT 返回 400 Invalid XML Content\n\n**原因**: ISAPI 要求 `WhiteBalanceStyle` 使用小写 `manual`/`auto`，不是首字母大写\n\n**解决**: 使用 `.lower()` 确保小写格式\n\n**代码位置**: `src/api/router.py` 第 2700 行附近\n\n---\n\n## LRN-20260614-002: 降噪 XML 完整结构\n\n**问题**: 降噪设置 XML 格式不完整\n\n**原因**: 缺少 `<mode>general</mode>` 和 `<GeneralMode>` 包装\n\n**解决**: 使用完整 ISAPI 结构:\n```xml\n<NoiseReduce version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"...\">\n<mode>general</mode>\n<GeneralMode>\n<generalLevel>{level}</generalLevel>\n</GeneralMode>\n</NoiseReduce>\n```\n\n**代码位置**: `src/api/router.py` 第 2770 行附近","path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\.learnings\\LEARNINGS.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":49621,"output":273,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49894,"cost":{"input":0.049621,"output":0.0008736000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0504946}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781392135259,"responseId":"cht000dff08@dx19ec33edd7cba5e412"}}
