{"type":"message","id":"e00fd8f9","parentId":"1df9681f","timestamp":"2026-06-13T23:09:06.571Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老板，**v6.52 修复完成！**\n\n## 修复总结\n\n### 问题\n1. 画面设置 B（蓝增益）和 R（红增益）参数设置后无提示、数值不固定\n2. 空域降噪、时域降噪没有起作用\n\n### 根本原因\n1. **白平衡**: ISAPI 要求 `WhiteBalanceStyle` 使用小写 `manual`/`auto`，代码使用了大写\n2. **降噪**: XML 格式不完整，缺少 `<mode>general</mode>` 和 `<GeneralMode>` 结构\n\n### 修复内容\n- `src/api/router.py`: 修复白平衡和降噪 XML 格式\n- `src/web/index.html`: 版本号 v6.45 → v6.52\n\n### 测试结果\n- **白平衡 R/B**: 5/5 全部通过 ✅\n- **降噪设置**: 5/5 全部通过 ✅\n\n**备份位置**: `backup_20260614_065730/`"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":49927,"output":221,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50148,"cost":{"input":0.049927,"output":0.0007072000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0506342}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781392142658,"responseId":"cht000d001c@dx19ec33ef5aeb85f582"}}
