{"type":"message","id":"c654081d","parentId":"afe4c0ed","timestamp":"2026-06-13T23:16:05.370Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"更新每日记忆："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c68bde6582604ff4bed0e20c","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 2026-06-14 开发日志\n\n## v6.52 画面控制修复\n\n### 问题描述\n1. 画面设置 B（蓝增益）和 R（红增益）参数设置后无提示、数值不固定\n2. 空域降噪、时域降噪没有起作用\n\n### 根本原因\n- 白平衡：ISAPI 要求小写 `manual`/`auto`，代码使用了首字母大写\n- 降噪：XML 结构不完整\n\n### 修复文件\n- `src/api/router.py`: set_whitebalance, set_noisereduce\n- `src/web/index.html`: 版本号 v6.52\n\n### 测试结果\n- 白平衡 R/B: 5/5 通过 ✅\n- 降噪设置: 5/5 通过 ✅\n\n### 备份\n- `backup_20260614_065730/`\n\n---\n\n## 关键教训\n\n1. **ISAPI XML 格式必须与 GET 响应一致**（大小写敏感）\n2. **降噪需要完整 XML 结构**（mode + GeneralMode）\n3. **ISAPI 端点验证流程**：GET 对比 → PUT 测试 → 连续验证","path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\memory\\2026-06-14.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":52886,"output":303,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53189,"cost":{"input":0.052885999999999996,"output":0.0009696,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.053855599999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781392550669,"responseId":"cht000d2cad@dx19ec34543dbb85e102"}}
