{"type":"message","id":"959e595b","parentId":"ec747dee","timestamp":"2026-06-13T23:16:20.062Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-5bcefdb7ff9940a687cfa4028e5a6490","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# AstroHub 开发关键规则\n\n## ISAPI 接口规则\n\n### 1. XML 格式必须与 GET 响应一致\n- GET 响应就是 PUT 应用的正确格式模板\n- 大小写敏感：`manual`/`auto`（小写），不是 `Manual`/`Auto`\n- 完整结构：降噪需要 `<mode>general</mode><GeneralMode><generalLevel>`\n\n### 2. 白平衡端点\n- GET: `/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/whiteBalance`\n- 返回字段：`WhiteBalanceStyle`, `WhiteBalanceRed`, `WhiteBalanceBlue`\n- PUT 格式必须与 GET 一致\n\n### 3. 降噪端点\n- GET: `/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/noiseReduce`\n- 返回字段：`mode`, `GeneralMode/generalLevel`\n- PUT 需要完整 `<mode>general</mode><GeneralMode>` 结构\n\n---\n\n## 测试验证标准\n\n### 连续5次测试\n- 每次设置不同值\n- 每次等待1秒\n- ISAPI PUT 返回 200\n- GET 验证值正确","path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\MEMORY.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":51478,"output":277,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51755,"cost":{"input":0.051477999999999996,"output":0.0008864000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0523644}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781392570623,"responseId":"cht000d33b4@dx19ec345816cb894142"}}
