{"type":"message","id":"32c0abd4","parentId":"51fda542","timestamp":"2026-06-13T23:16:27.223Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老板，复盘和记忆更新完成！\n\n## 复盘总结\n\n### 发现的问题\n| 问题 | 根本原因 | 修复 |\n|------|----------|------|\n| 白平衡 R/B 设置失败 | ISAPI 要求小写 `manual`/`auto` | 使用 `.lower()` |\n| 降噪设置无效 | XML 结构不完整 | 添加完整 `<mode>general</mode><GeneralMode>` |\n\n### 教训写入位置\n- ✅ `.learnings/LEARNINGS.md` - 详细教训\n- ✅ `memory/2026-06-14.md` - 每日日志\n- ✅ `MEMORY.md` - 长期规则\n\n### 核心教训\n**ISAPI XML 格式必须与 GET 响应一致** — GET 响应就是 PUT 的正确模板，包括大小写和节点结构。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":53686,"output":184,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53870,"cost":{"input":0.053686,"output":0.0005888,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0542748}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781392580079,"responseId":"cht000d4773@dx19ec345a257ba5c342"}}
{"type":"message","id":"17cd1365","parentId":"32c0abd4","timestamp":"2026-06-13T23:26:29.005Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:8447197723\",\n  \"message_id\": \"35316\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-06-14 07:26 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yixing Zhang (8447197723)\",\n  \"id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"name\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"username\": \"ZhangyixingTG\"\n}\n```\n\n测试结果\n\n白平衡 R/B 设置：5/5 通过 ✅\n\n• 测试 1: R=80, B=60 -> PASS\n• 测试 2: R=100, B=75 -> PASS\n• 测试 3: R=120, B=90 -> PASS\n• 测试 4: R=140, B=105 -> PASS\n• 测试 5: R=160, B=120 -> PASS\n\n降噪设置：5/5 通过 ✅\n\n• 测试 1: level=30 -> PASS\n• 测试 2: level=45 -> PASS\n• 测试 3: level=60 -> PASS\n• 测试 4: level=75 -> PASS\n• 测试 5: level=90 -> PASS\n\n你这个测试，是设置这些值，还是设置，然后读取返回值？"}],"timestamp":1781393189001}}
{"type":"message","id":"5c3a8c26","parentId":"17cd1365","timestamp":"2026-06-13T23:26:35.576Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老板，我的测试流程是：\n\n**设置 → 读取验证**\n\n具体流程：\n1. **PUT** 设置值到 ISAPI 端点\n2. **GET** 从 ISAPI 端点读取当前值\n3. **对比** GET 返回的值是否等于设置的值\n\n举例：\n```\n测试 1: R=80, B=60\n  → PUT WhiteBalanceRed=80, WhiteBalanceBlue=60\n  → GET WhiteBalance\n  → 对比返回值: Red=80, Blue=60 ✓ PASS\n```\n\n所以测试验证的是：**设置值后，设备实际存储的值是否正确**。\n\n不是只测试 API 返回 200，而是验证设备状态真正改变了。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":52309,"output":154,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52463,"cost":{"input":0.052308999999999994,"output":0.0004928,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.052801799999999996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781393189006,"responseId":"cht000d9602@dx19ec34eeba6b91a742"}}
{"type":"message","id":"dd1df355","parentId":"5c3a8c26","timestamp":"2026-06-13T23:27:07.327Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:8447197723\",\n  \"message_id\": \"35318\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-06-14 07:27 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yixing Zhang (8447197723)\",\n  \"id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"name\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"username\": \"ZhangyixingTG\"\n}\n```\n\n降噪设置，是空域时域分开，还是统一一个降噪？这是不同端点"}],"timestamp":1781393227323}}
{"type":"message","id":"61383f93","parentId":"dd1df355","timestamp":"2026-06-13T23:27:16.148Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老板，让我检查设备的实际降噪端点结构："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6dc46fb5b5a54d68b3e20278","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd astrohub; python -c \"\nimport os\nos.environ.pop('http_proxy', None)\nimport requests\nfrom requests.auth import HTTPDigestAuth\n\nip = '192.168.5.72'\nauth = HTTPDigestAuth('admin', 'Nftw1357')\nbase = f'http://{ip}/ISAPI'\n\nprint('=== 检查降噪相关端点 ===')\nprint()\n\n# 当前 noiseReduce 端点\nr = requests.get(f'{base}/Image/channels/1/noiseReduce', auth=auth, timeout=10, proxies={'http':None,'https':None})\nprint('1. noiseReduce 端点:')\nprint(r.text)\nprint()\n\n# 检查是否有空域/时域分开的端点\nendpoints = [\n    '/Image/channels/1/spatialDenoise',\n    '/Image/channels/1/temporalDenoise',\n    '/Image/channels/1/spatialNoiseReduce',\n    '/Image/channels/1/temporalNoiseReduce',\n    '/Image/channels/1/denoise/spatial',\n    '/Image/channels/1/denoise/temporal',\n    '/Image/channels/1/noiseReduce/spatial',\n    '/Image/channels/1/noiseReduce/temporal',\n]\n\nprint('2. 其他可能的端点:')\nfor ep in endpoints:\n    r = requests.get(f'{base}{ep}', auth=auth, timeout=5, proxies={'http':None,'https':None})\n    print(f'   {ep}: {r.status_code}')\n\" 2>&1","timeout":30,"workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":52826,"output":373,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53199,"cost":{"input":0.052826,"output":0.0011936000000000002,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0540196}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781393227328,"responseId":"cht000d9883@dx19ec34f8ca0b85e102"}}
