{"type":"message","id":"7d018f65","parentId":"a0a221fc","timestamp":"2026-06-13T23:27:36.492Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老板，**前端代码有空域和时域两个滑动条**，但**设备 ISAPI 只有一个统一的 `generalLevel`**！\n\n这是设计问题：\n- 前端：空域滑动条 + 时域滑动条\n- 后端：把两个值都映射到同一个 `generalLevel`\n\n**这意味着空域和时域实际设置的是同一个值**，用户以为分开控制，实际是同步的。\n\n我需要确认：**您想修复成什么样？**\n\n选项：\n1. **保持现状**：空域/时域都设置同一个值（简单但用户可能困惑）\n2. **隐藏时域**：只显示一个\"降噪\"滑动条\n3. **检查设备是否支持分开**：有些高端设备支持，需要查看 ISAPI 文档\n\n您想要哪种方案？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":57838,"output":170,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":58008,"cost":{"input":0.057838,"output":0.000544,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.058382}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781393248178,"responseId":"cht000d0fbe@dx19ec34fd3d9b828232"}}
{"type":"message","id":"b5e1fd82","parentId":"7d018f65","timestamp":"2026-06-13T23:28:00.330Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:8447197723\",\n  \"message_id\": \"35322\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-06-14 07:27 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yixing Zhang (8447197723)\",\n  \"id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"name\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"username\": \"ZhangyixingTG\"\n}\n```\n\n这个设备支持时域空域降噪，所有设备都支持，继续查询官方文档，你的测试没有完成"}],"timestamp":1781393280321}}
{"type":"message","id":"2329ca32","parentId":"b5e1fd82","timestamp":"2026-06-13T23:28:14.546Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老板，我继续查询 ISAPI 文档，找到正确的空域/时域降噪端点："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-de58e4fc1bea4ee485ac909ec153d3bd","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd astrohub; python -c \"\nimport os\nos.environ.pop('http_proxy', None)\nimport requests\nfrom requests.auth import HTTPDigestAuth\n\nip = '192.168.5.72'\nauth = HTTPDigestAuth('admin', 'Nftw1357')\nbase = f'http://{ip}/ISAPI'\n\nprint('=== 深入检查降噪端点结构 ===')\nprint()\n\n# 1. 检查 noiseReduce 的完整结构\nr = requests.get(f'{base}/Image/channels/1/noiseReduce', auth=auth, timeout=10, proxies={'http':None,'https':None})\nprint('1. 当前 noiseReduce 响应:')\nprint(r.text)\nprint()\n\n# 2. 检查 capabilities 看是否有更多模式\nr = requests.get(f'{base}/Image/channels/1/capabilities', auth=auth, timeout=10, proxies={'http':None,'https':None})\nprint('2. Image capabilities:')\nif r.status_code == 200:\n    print(r.text[:1000])\nprint()\n\n# 3. 检查是否有 expert 模式的降噪\nendpoints = [\n    '/Image/channels/1/noiseReduce/expert',\n    '/Image/channels/1/noiseReduce/ExpertMode',\n    '/Image/channels/1/noiseReduction',\n    '/Image/channels/1/NoiseReduction',\n]\n\nprint('3. 其他降噪端点:')\nfor ep in endpoints:\n    r = requests.get(f'{base}{ep}', auth=auth, timeout=5, proxies={'http':None,'https':None})\n    print(f'   {ep}: {r.status_code}')\n    if r.status_code == 200:\n        print(f'   内容: {r.text[:300]}')\n\" 2>&1","timeout":30,"workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":56056,"output":435,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56491,"cost":{"input":0.056055999999999995,"output":0.0013920000000000002,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.05744799999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781393280331,"responseId":"cht000daaaa@dx19ec3505586b9ca102"}}
{"type":"message","id":"033e3571","parentId":"2329ca32","timestamp":"2026-06-13T23:28:15.347Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-de58e4fc1bea4ee485ac909ec153d3bd","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[31;1mC:\\Python\\Lib\\site-packages\\requests\\__init__.py:113: RequestsDependencyWarning: urllib3 (2.1.0) or chardet (7.2.0)/charset_normalizer (3.4.6) doesn't match a supported version![0m\r\n[31;1m  warnings.warn([0m\r\n=== �����齵��˵�ṹ ===\r\n\r\n1. ��ǰ noiseReduce ��Ӧ:\r\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\r\r\n<NoiseReduce version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">\r\r\n<mode>general</mode>\r\r\n<GeneralMode>\r\r\n<generalLevel>90</generalLevel>\r\r\n</GeneralMode>\r\r\n</NoiseReduce>\r\r\n\r\n\r\n2. Image capabilities:\r\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\r\r\n<ImageChannel version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">\r\r\n<id>1</id>\r\r\n<enabled>true</enabled>\r\r\n<videoInputID>1</videoInputID>\r\r\n<WDR>\r\r\n<mode opt=\"close,open\">close</mode>\r\r\n<WDRLevel min=\"0\" max=\"100\">50</WDRLevel>\r\r\n</WDR>\r\r\n<BLC>\r\r\n<enabled opt=\"true,false\">false</enabled>\r\r\n<BLCMode opt=\"CLOSE,UP,DOWN,LEFT,RIGHT,CENTER,AUTO\">CLOSE</BLCMode>\r\r\n</BLC>\r\r\n<IrcutFilter>\r\r\n<IrcutFilterType opt=\"day,night,auto,schedule\">auto</IrcutFilterType>\r\r\n<nightToDayFilterLevel opt=\"1,2,3,4,5,6,7\">4</nightToDayFilterLevel>\r\r\n<Schedule>\r\r\n<scheduleType opt=\"day,night\">day</scheduleType>\r\r\n<TimeRange>\r\r\n<beginTime>07:00:00</beginTime>\r\r\n<endTime>18:00:00</endTime>\r\r\n</TimeRange>\r\r\n</Schedule>\r\r\n</IrcutFilter>\r\r\n<WhiteBalance>\r\r\n<WhiteBalanceStyle opt=\"manual,locked,outdoor,indoor,daylightLamp,sodiumlight,autotrace,auto\">manual</WhiteBalanceStyle>\r\r\n<WhiteBalanceRed min=\"0\" max=\"255\">160</WhiteBalanceRed>\r\r\n<WhiteBalanceBlue min=\"0\" max=\"255\">120</WhiteBalanceBlue>\r\n\r\n3. ��������˵�:\r\n   /Image/channels/1/noiseReduce/