{"type":"message","id":"62351b51","parentId":"329aa5d1","timestamp":"2026-06-13T23:32:04.542Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"更新 HEARTBEAT："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c651870744374f8880c0a521","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 心跳与任务状态\n\n**最后更新**: 2026-06-14 07:35\n**状态**: v6.53 空域/时域降噪修复完成\n**工作空间**: C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\n\n### v6.53 修复内容\n\n| # | 问题 | 修复 | 文件 |\n|---|------|------|------|\n| 1 | 降噪使用 general 模式，空域/时域同步 | 改用 advanced 模式，空域/时域分开 | `src/api/router.py` |\n| 2 | 版本号更新 | v6.52 → v6.53 | `src/web/index.html` |\n\n### ISAPI 降噪模式\n\n设备支持三种模式：\n- `close` - 关闭降噪\n- `general` - 统一降噪（空域=时域）\n- `advanced` - 分开控制\n\n**advanced 模式字段**：\n- `FrameNoiseReduceLevel` = 空域降噪（帧内）\n- `InterFrameNoiseReduceLevel` = 时域降噪（帧间）\n\n### 测试验证\n\n**空域/时域降噪分开设置**: 5/5 通过 ✅\n- 测试不同空域/时域值组合\n- PUT=200，GET验证值正确\n\n### 备份位置\n- `backup_20260614_065730/`","path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\HEARTBEAT.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":67265,"output":352,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67617,"cost":{"input":0.06726499999999999,"output":0.0011264,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.06839139999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781393502363,"responseId":"cht000ebcb6@dx19ec353da87b893102"}}
