{"type":"message","id":"2f61487a","parentId":"6937ae91","timestamp":"2026-06-13T23:51:42.486Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"降噪设置的 toast 提示已经正常。\n\n但是有个问题：**降噪只发送一个参数（spatial_level 或 temporal_level），后端需要同时发送两个值才能正确设置**。\n\n让我检查后端代码是否正确处理只传一个参数的情况："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-848fe700c4274741a832429ebfae2a85","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":25,"offset":2775,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\api\\router.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":68192,"output":99,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68291,"cost":{"input":0.068192,"output":0.0003168,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.06850880000000001}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781394694255,"responseId":"cht000d8fd0@dx19ec365ee00ba5e412"}}
{"type":"message","id":"aedd588d","parentId":"2f61487a","timestamp":"2026-06-13T23:51:42.493Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-848fe700c4274741a832429ebfae2a85","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\r\n    target_ip = _resolve_device_id_to_ip(mgr, device_id)\r\n    if not target_ip:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"无法解析设备标识: {device_id}\"}\r\n\r\n    ctrl, err = mgr._get_controller(target_ip)\r\n    if err:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": err}\r\n\r\n    client = ctrl.client\r\n    try:\r\n        # 构造降噪 XML - 使用 advanced 模式支持空域/时域分开\r\n        spatial = data.get(\"spatial_level\", 50)\r\n        temporal = data.get(\"temporal_level\", 50)\r\n        \r\n        # ISAPI advanced 模式: FrameNoiseReduceLevel = 空域, InterFrameNoiseReduceLevel = 时域\r\n        xml_str = f'''<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\r\n<NoiseReduce version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">\r\n<mode>advanced</mode>\r\n<AdvancedMode>\r\n<FrameNoiseReduceLevel>{spatial}</FrameNoiseReduceLevel>\r\n<InterFrameNoiseReduceLevel>{temporal}</InterFrameNoiseReduceLevel>\r\n</AdvancedMode>\r\n</NoiseReduce>'''\r\n\r\n\n[520 more lines in file. Use offset=2800 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781394702493}}
{"type":"message","id":"3ad8bb27","parentId":"aedd588d","timestamp":"2026-06-13T23:51:57.344Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"问题：后端使用默认值 50，前端只传一个参数时，另一个参数会被覆盖为 50。\n\n需要修复：后端应该先获取当前值，只更新传入的参数："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f0a969bc77194725b907cfc5","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"    client = ctrl.client\n    try:\n        # 先获取当前降噪设置\n        current_spatial = 50\n        current_temporal = 50\n        \n        resp = client.get(\"/Image/channels/1/noiseReduce\")\n        if resp.status_code == 200:\n            import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\n            root = ET.fromstring(resp.xml)\n            for elem in root.iter():\n                tag = elem.tag.split(\"}\")[-1] if \"}\" in elem.tag else elem.tag\n                if tag == \"FrameNoiseReduceLevel\":\n                    current_spatial = int(elem.text or 50)\n                elif tag == \"InterFrameNoiseReduceLevel\":\n                    current_temporal = int(elem.text or 50)\n        \n        # 使用传入值或当前值\n        spatial = data.get(\"spatial_level\", current_spatial)\n        temporal = data.get(\"temporal_level\", current_temporal)\n        \n        # ISAPI advanced 模式: FrameNoiseReduceLevel = 空域, InterFrameNoiseReduceLevel = 时域\n        xml_str = f'''<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<NoiseReduce version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">\n<mode>advanced</mode>\n<AdvancedMode>\n<FrameNoiseReduceLevel>{spatial}</FrameNoiseReduceLevel>\n<InterFrameNoiseReduceLevel>{temporal}</InterFrameNoiseReduceLevel>\n</AdvancedMode>\n</NoiseReduce>'''\n\n","oldText":"    client = ctrl.client\n    try:\n        # 构造降噪 XML - 使用 advanced 模式支持空域/时域分开\n        spatial = data.get(\"spatial_level\", 50)\n        temporal = data.get(\"temporal_level\", 50)\n        \n        # ISAPI advanced 模式: FrameNoiseReduceLevel = 空域, InterFrameNoiseReduceLevel = 时域\n        xml_str = f'''<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<NoiseReduce version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">\n<mode>advanced</mode>\n<AdvancedMode>\n<FrameNoiseReduceLevel>{spatial}</FrameNoiseReduceLevel>\n<InterFrameNoiseReduceLevel>{temporal}</InterFrameNoiseReduceLevel>\n</AdvancedMode>\n</NoiseReduce>'''\n\n"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\api\\router.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":71804,"output":635,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":72439,"cost":{"input":0.07180399999999999,"output":0.0020320000000000004,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.073836}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781394702494,"responseId":"cht000d83b6@dx19ec3660732b958232"}}
