{"type":"message","id":"e36f19f0","parentId":"b0ad15c5","timestamp":"2026-06-14T00:17:31.882Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-68bacc817dad48c393649296c4ebe01c","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"function setWhiteBalanceGain(channel, value) {\n    var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\n    if (!dev) return;\n    \n    // v5.46: 先切换到手动模式再调整增益\n    var wbModeSelect = document.getElementById('wbMode');\n    if (wbModeSelect && wbModeSelect.value !== 'manual') {\n        wbModeSelect.value = 'manual';\n        apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/image/whitebalance', { mode: 'manual' });\n        // 启用滑动条\n        var wbRed = document.getElementById('wbRed');\n        var wbBlue = document.getElementById('wbBlue');\n        if (wbRed) wbRed.disabled = false;\n        if (wbBlue) wbBlue.disabled = false;\n    }\n    \n    // 更新显示\n    if (channel === 'red') {\n        var el = document.getElementById('wbRedVal');\n        if (el) el.textContent = value;\n    } else {\n        var el = document.getElementById('wbBlueVal');\n        if (el) el.textContent = value;\n    }\n    \n    // 发送请求\n    var key = channel === 'red' ? 'red_gain' : 'blue_gain';\n    var label = channel === 'red' ? 'R (红增益)' : 'B (蓝增益)';\n    apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/image/whitebalance', { [key]: parseInt(value) })\n        .then(function(r) {\n            if (r && r.success) {\n                showToast('success', label + ': ' + value);\n            }\n        });\n}\n\n// 设置降噪\nfunction setNoiseReduce(type, value) {\n    var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\n    if (!dev) return;\n    \n    var el = document.getElementById(type === 'spatial' ? 'dnrSpatialVal' : 'dnrTemporalVal');\n    if (el) el.textContent = value;\n    \n    var key = type === 'spatial' ? 'spatial_level' : 'temporal_level';\n\n[182 more lines in file. Use offset=965 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781396251882}}
{"type":"message","id":"9b91618b","parentId":"e36f19f0","timestamp":"2026-06-14T00:17:59.979Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"前端代码逻辑分析：\n\n### 问题发现\n\n**白平衡 R/B 设置问题**：\n\n第 925-932 行：当 `wbModeSelect.value !== 'manual'` 时，会先发送 `{ mode: 'manual' }` 请求，然后立即在第 945-949 行发送 `{ red_gain/blue_gain: value }` 请求。\n\n**问题**：这两个请求是**异步并发**发送的，可能导致：\n1. 第一个请求 `{ mode: 'manual' }` 后端获取当前值时，设备可能还是 auto 模式\n2. 第二个请求 `{ red_gain: value }` 同时到达，后端获取当前值时可能还没收到第一个请求的结果\n\n**修复方案**：当需要切换模式时，应该等待模式切换完成后再发送增益设置请求。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-8f62c18b35324137891e9a024100ef0f","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"function setWhiteBalanceGain(channel, value) {\n    var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\n    if (!dev) return;\n    \n    // 更新显示\n    if (channel === 'red') {\n        var el = document.getElementById('wbRedVal');\n        if (el) el.textContent = value;\n    } else {\n        var el = document.getElementById('wbBlueVal');\n        if (el) el.textContent = value;\n    }\n    \n    var key = channel === 'red' ? 'red_gain' : 'blue_gain';\n    var label = channel === 'red' ? 'R (红增益)' : 'B (蓝增益)';\n    \n    // v6.55: 检查是否需要先切换到手动模式\n    var wbModeSelect = document.getElementById('wbMode');\n    if (wbModeSelect && wbModeSelect.value !== 'manual') {\n        // 先切换模式，等待完成后再设置增益\n        wbModeSelect.value = 'manual';\n        apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/image/whitebalance', { mode: 'manual' })\n            .then(function(r) {\n                if (r && r.success) {\n                    // 启用滑动条\n                    var wbRed = document.getElementById('wbRed');\n                    var wbBlue = document.getElementById('wbBlue');\n                    if (wbRed) wbRed.disabled = false;\n                    if (wbBlue) wbBlue.disabled = false;\n                    \n                    // 模式切换完成后再设置增益\n                    apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/image/whitebalance', { [key]: parseInt(value) })\n                        .then(function(r2) {\n                            if (r2 && r2.success) {\n                                showToast('success', label + ': ' + value);\n                            }\n                        });\n                }\n            });\n    } else {\n        // 已经是手动模式，直接设置增益\n        apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/image/whitebalance', { [key]: parseInt(value) })\n            .then(function(r) {\n                if (r && r.success) {\n                    showToast('success', label + ': ' + value);\n                }\n            });\n    }\n}","oldText":"function setWhiteBalanceGain(channel, value) {\n    var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\n    if (!dev) return;\n    \n    // v5.46: 先切换到手动模式再调整增益\n    var wbModeSelect = document.getElementById('wbMode');\n    if (wbModeSelect && wbModeSelect.value !== 'manual') {\n        wbModeSelect.value = 'manual';\n        apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/image/whitebalance', { mode: 'manual' });\n        // 启用滑动条\n        var wbRed = document.getElementById('wbRed');\n        var wbBlue = document.getElementById('wbBlue');\n        if (wbRed) wbRed.disabled = false;\n        if (wbBlue) wbBlue.disabled = false;\n    }\n    \n    // 更新显示\n    if (channel === 'red') {\n        var el = document.getElementById('wbRedVal');\n        if (el) el.textContent = value;\n    } else {\n        var el = document.getElementById('wbBlueVal');\n        if (el) el.textContent = value;\n    }\n    \n    // 发送请求\n    var key = channel === 'red' ? 'red_gain' : 'blue_gain';\n    var label = channel === 'red' ? 'R (红增益)' : 'B (蓝增益)';\n    apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/image/whitebalance', { [key]: parseInt(value) })\n        .then(function(r) {\n            if (r && r.success) {\n                showToast('success', label + ': ' + value);\n            }\n        });\n}"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}}