{"type":"message","id":"4ed73de1","parentId":"86132d71","timestamp":"2026-06-14T00:18:21.805Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在更新 HEARTBEAT："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c18abe61b159412e9030407e","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 心跳与任务状态\n\n**最后更新**: 2026-06-14 08:25\n**状态**: v6.55 白平衡 R/B 异步修复完成\n**工作空间**: C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\n\n### v6.55 修复内容\n\n| # | 问题 | 修复 | 文件 |\n|---|------|------|------|\n| 1 | 白平衡 R/B 设置时模式切换和增益设置并发导致失效 | 改为顺序执行：先切换模式，等待完成后再设置增益 | `console.html` |\n| 2 | 版本号更新 | v6.54 → v6.55 | `index.html` |\n\n### 问题分析\n\n**原代码问题**：\n```javascript\n// 模式切换请求（异步）\napiPost(..., { mode: 'manual' });\n// 增益设置请求（异步，与上面并发）\napiPost(..., { red_gain: value });\n```\n\n两个请求并发发送，后端可能同时获取当前值，导致设置失效。\n\n**修复后**：\n```javascript\n// 先切换模式，等待完成\napiPost(..., { mode: 'manual' }).then(function() {\n    // 模式切换完成后再设置增益\n    apiPost(..., { red_gain: value });\n});\n```\n\n### E2E 测试结果\n\n- ISAPI 层：白平衡 R/B 分开 ✅，降噪空域/时域分开 ✅\n- 后端逻辑：白平衡 R/B 分开 ✅，降噪空域/时域分开 ✅\n\n### 备份位置\n- `backup_20260614_065730/`\n- `backup_20260614_081500/`","path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\HEARTBEAT.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":86654,"output":419,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":87073,"cost":{"input":0.086654,"output":0.0013408,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0879948}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781396287009,"responseId":"cht000d7396@dx19ec37e3c16ba5e412"}}
