{"type":"message","id":"65aad5e1","parentId":"89706225","timestamp":"2026-06-14T00:20:42.060Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:8447197723\",\n  \"message_id\": \"35370\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-06-14 08:20 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yixing Zhang (8447197723)\",\n  \"id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"name\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"username\": \"ZhangyixingTG\"\n}\n```\n\n你现在给我搞清楚，下拉菜单已经切换了模式，变成了手动模式。后续发送R B值，为什么还要单独发一条manual？"}],"timestamp":1781396442056}}
