{"type":"message","id":"d2e0a7ed","parentId":"00387f47","timestamp":"2026-06-14T00:20:50.440Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_edd60ca2c8d64867978f5a16","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"function setWhiteBalanceGain(channel, value) {\n    var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\n    if (!dev) return;\n    \n    // 更新显示\n    if (channel === 'red') {\n        var el = document.getElementById('wbRedVal');\n        if (el) el.textContent = value;\n    } else {\n        var el = document.getElementById('wbBlueVal');\n        if (el) el.textContent = value;\n    }\n    \n    var key = channel === 'red' ? 'red_gain' : 'blue_gain';\n    var label = channel === 'red' ? 'R (红增益)' : 'B (蓝增益)';\n    \n    // v6.55: 检查是否需要先切换到手动模式\n    var wbModeSelect = document.getElementById('wbMode');\n    if (wbModeSelect && wbModeSelect.value !== 'manual') {\n        // 先切换模式，等待完成后再设置增益\n        wbModeSelect.value = 'manual';\n        apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/image/whitebalance', { mode: 'manual' })\n            .then(function(r) {\n                if (r && r.success) {\n                    // 启用滑动条\n                    var wbRed = document.getElementById('wbRed');\n                    var wbBlue = document.getElementById('wbBlue');\n                    if (wbRed) wbRed.disabled = false;\n                    if (wbBlue) wbBlue.disabled = false;\n                    \n                    // 模式切换完成后再设置增益\n                    apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/image/whitebalance', { [key]: parseInt(value) })\n                        .then(function(r2) {\n                            if (r2 && r2.success) {\n                                showToast('success', label + ': ' + value);\n                            }\n                        });\n                }\n            });\n    } else {\n        // 已经是手动模式，直接设置增益\n        apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/image/whitebalance', { [key]: parseInt(value) })\n            .then(function(r) {\n                if (r && r.success) {\n                    showToast('success', label + ': ' + value);\n                }\n            });\n    }\n}\n\n\n[191 more lines in file. Use offset=970 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781396450440}}
{"type":"message","id":"3a36a5e4","parentId":"d2e0a7ed","timestamp":"2026-06-14T00:21:02.610Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老板，我看清楚了！\n\n**当前逻辑**：\n- 第 939-941 行：检查 `wbModeSelect.value !== 'manual'`\n- 只有当**下拉菜单不是手动模式**时，才发送 `{ mode: 'manual' }`\n\n**问题场景**：\n如果用户已经通过下拉菜单切换到手动模式，那么：\n1. 下拉菜单已经发送了 `{ mode: 'manual' }`（通过 `setWhiteBalanceMode` 函数）\n2. 用户调整 R/B 滑动条时，`wbModeSelect.value === 'manual'`，所以不会再发送 manual\n\n**这个逻辑是正确的！** 不会重复发送 manual。\n\n但您说\"后续发送 R B 值，为什么还要单独发一条 manual\"？\n\n让我检查 `setWhiteBalanceMode` 函数，看看下拉菜单切换时是否也有问题："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-de56fc346cd049ddb4e83b3b3cb40247","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":30,"offset":892,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":84559,"output":226,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":84785,"cost":{"input":0.084559,"output":0.0007232,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.08528219999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781396450442,"responseId":"cht000d772e@dx19ec380bf2bb91a742"}}
{"type":"message","id":"04a0c8c1","parentId":"3a36a5e4","timestamp":"2026-06-14T00:21:02.619Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-de56fc346cd049ddb4e83b3b3cb40247","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"function setWhiteBalanceMode(mode) {\n    var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\n    if (!dev) return;\n    \n    // v5.40: 处理三种模式\n    var actualMode = mode;\n    if (mode === 'auto_official') {\n        actualMode = 'auto';\n    } else if (mode === 'auto_astrohub') {\n        // 暂未实现\n        showToast('warning', '自动暂未实现');\n        return;\n    }\n    \n    apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/image/whitebalance', { mode: actualMode })\n        .then(function(r) {\n            if (r && r.success) {\n                showToast('success', '白平衡: ' + (actualMode === 'auto' ? '自动（官方）' : '手动'));\n                // v5.40: 更新 R/B 滑动条状态\n                var wbRed = document.getElementById('wbRed');\n                var wbBlue = document.getElementById('wbBlue');\n                if (wbRed) wbRed.disabled = actualMode !== 'manual';\n                if (wbBlue) wbBlue.disabled = actualMode !== 'manual';\n            }\n        });\n}\n\n// 设置白平衡增益 R/B\nfunction setWhiteBalanceGain(channel, value) {\n    var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\n\n[239 more lines in file. Use offset=922 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781396462619}}
{"type":"message","id":"dfa4e768","parentId":"04a0c8c1","timestamp":"2026-06-14T00:21:13.144Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"老板，我看明白了！**代码逻辑是正确的**：\n\n1. **下拉菜单切换到手动**：`setWhiteBalanceMode('manual')` 只发送 `{ mode: 'manual' }`\n2. **调整 R/B 滑动条**：`setWhiteBalanceGain` 检查 `wbModeSelect.value === 'manual'`，已经是手动就不会再发送 manual\n\n**不会重复发送 manual！**\n\n**如果您看到了重复发送 manual 的情况**，可能是：\n1. 下拉菜单切换时，设备还没返回成功，用户就立即拖动滑动条\n2. 或者我理解错了您的问题\n\n请告诉我：\n1. 您是在什么场景下看到\"发送 R B 值时还发送了 manual\"？\n2. 是在浏览器开发者工具 Network 面板看到的吗？\n\n我需要确认具体问题才能精确修复。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":89077,"output":181,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":89258,"cost":{"input":0.08907699999999999,"output":0.0005792000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.08965619999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781396462622,"responseId":"cht000d7dbc@dx19ec380e65cba5b442"}}
